properties.name: Durdixol

properties.name: Halicha
properties.meaning: Eht.: Hadicha

properties.name: Halovat
properties.meaning: Zavq, lazzar; osoyishta, tinch

properties.name: Halol
properties.meaning: Toza, pokiza; qonuniy

properties.name: Halqa
properties.meaning: Halqalangan, bog‘langan; mahkam, mustahkam, berk. Chaqaloqni o‘limdan asrash maqsadida beriluvchi ism

properties.name: Hamdam
properties.meaning: Do‘st, o‘rtoq, sodiq, vafodor do‘st. Otasiga, boshqa bolalarga do‘st, esh bolib yursin

properties.name: Hamdambo‘l
properties.meaning: Otasiga va o‘zini oldingi aka-opalariga yo‘ldosh, esh bo‘lib yursin

properties.name: Hamdamxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamdam va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Hamdamqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamdam (Hamdam+qul)

properties.name: Hamdo‘st
properties.meaning: Hamdam, do‘st, hamkor, mustahkam, sodiq do‘st

properties.name: Hamza
properties.meaning: o‘tkir, achchiq, kuydiruvchi, yondiruvchi, chirog‘ yoki dorivor o‘simlik nomi. Bu nom Muhammad (sav) tog‘asining ismi bolgan. Shakllari: Hamzaxon, Hamzaqul, Hamzaxoja

properties.name: Hamzaali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamza va Ali

properties.name: Hamzamurod
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamza va Murod

properties.name: Hamzqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamza (Hamza+qul)

properties.name: Hamid
properties.meaning: Maqtovchi, madh qiluvchi, Allohga hamdu sano aytuvchi, shukur qiluvchi yoki hamid - issiq, qaynoq. Bu nom Muhammad (sav)ning sifatlaridan biridir. Asli: Hamidulla (qar.). Shakllari: Hamidbek, Hamidjon, Hamidxon

properties.name: Hamidali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamid va Ali

properties.name: Hamiddin
properties.meaning: Dinni madh qiluvchi

properties.name: Hamidulla
properties.meaning: Allohning madhu sanosi; maqtovi; shonu shavkati yoki Allohning maqtovga loyiq bandasi

properties.name: Hamidxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan maqtovga, olqishga loyiq bola

properties.name: Hamidqul
properties.meaning: Maqtovga sazovorning, ya’ni Muhammadning quli

properties.name: Hammod
properties.meaning: Ulug‘lovchi madh etuvchi yoki e’zozga loyiq

properties.name: Hamro
properties.meaning: Yo‘ldosh,  esh, hamdam yoki qirmizi, qizil rangli. Shakllari: Hamroboy, Hamrojon, Hamroxon

properties.name: Hamrotosh
properties.meaning: Toshdek mustahkam bo‘lsin va o‘zgalarga esh, hamdam bo‘lib yursin

properties.name: Hamroxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamro va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Hamrosho
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamro va Sho(h)

properties.name: Hamroqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamro (Hamro+qul)

properties.name: Hamroqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Hamro va Qo‘zi

properties.name: Hanafiy
properties.meaning: Payg‘ambar avlodiga mansub yoki bo‘ysunuvchi, itoatkor

properties.name: Hanafiya
properties.meaning: Payg‘ambar nasliga mansub bola

properties.name: Hanjar
properties.meaning: Yo‘l, qoida, rasm-rusm. Eht.: Xanjar

properties.name: Haniya
properties.meaning: Haqiqiy poydor; asl, sof; pokiza

properties.name: Hanqa
properties.meaning: Honqada tug‘ilgan bola, Honqa farzandi

properties.name: Haris
properties.meaning: o‘ta berilgan, maftun bo‘lgan yoki sidqidil, maftunkor yoki mohir, uquvli

properties.name: Harif
properties.meaning: o‘rtoq, do‘st, ulfat yoki xushyor, nozik tab’

properties.name: Hasan
properties.meaning: Yaxshi, tuzuk; chiroyli, sohibjamol. Ba’zi manbalarda ezgulik, yaxshilik; fasohatli deb izohlanadi. Bu nom Ali ibn Tolibning Fotimadan tug‘ilgan o‘g‘li - Hasan ibn Ali (595-669)ning ismi bo‘lgan. Hasan - Muhammad (sav)ning nabirasidir. Shakllari: Hasanboy, Hasanjon, Hasanxon

properties.name: Hasanali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hasan va Ali

properties.name: Hasanmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Hasan va Mirza

properties.name: Hasanniyoz
properties.meaning: Alloh tuhfa qilgan chiroyli bola yoki Allohdan yolvorib so‘rab olingan

properties.name: Hasanpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Go‘zal, chiroyli va po‘latdek mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Hasantosh
properties.meaning: Chiroyli, go‘zal husnli bola toshdek mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Hasanto‘ra
properties.meaning: Qar. Hasan va To‘ra

properties.name: Hasanxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar, avliyozodalar naslidan bo‘lgan chiroyli bola

properties.name: Hasanqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hasan (Hasan+qul)

properties.name: Hasrat
properties.meaning: Qayg‘urib yurib, armon bilan erishilgan bola yoki onasi yosh o‘lib qolgan bola

properties.name: Hasratqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hasrat (Hasrat+qul)

properties.name: Hafiz
properties.meaning: Himoya qiluvchi, qo‘riqlovchi, o‘z panohida asrovchi. Bu nom Allohi Taoloning sifatlaridan biridir. Asli: Abduhafiz (qar.)

properties.name: Hafiza
properties.meaning: Qar. Hafiz (Hafiz+a)

properties.name: Hafiziddin
properties.meaning: Dinni avaylovchi, asrovchi, din posboni

properties.name: Hafizulla
properties.meaning: Alloh qo‘riqlaydigan, asraydigan bola; Allohning panohida, muhofazasida bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Hashmat, Hashamat
properties.meaning: Izzat-hurmatli, shonu shavkatli

properties.name: Haq
properties.meaning: Haqiqat, rost, haqiqatda mavjud, odil, adolatli. Bu nom Allohi Taoloning sifatlaridan biridir. Asli: Haqnazar, Haqberdi (qar.)

properties.name: Haqberdi
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatli, ya’ni Alloh ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Haqboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Haqberdi ismining eq.shakli

properties.name: Haqdod
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatli, ya’ni Alloh bergan bola

properties.name: Haqyor
properties.meaning: Alloh qo‘llab-qo‘ltiqlaydigan, madadkor bo‘ladigan bola

properties.name: Haqmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Haqmirza yoki odil, adolatli; kotib, hukmdor

properties.name: Haqmurod
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatli, ya’ni Alloh erishtirgan orzu, maqsad

properties.name: Haqnazar
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatlining iltifoti, e’tibori bo‘lgan bola yoki Allohning etibori (nazari) tushgan bola

properties.name: Haqniyoz
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatli, ya’ni Alloh bergan tuhfa, ehson

properties.name: Haqpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Qar. Haq va Po‘lat

properties.name: Haqturdi
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan bola turadi, yashaydi, deb umidvormiz

properties.name: Haqqul
properties.meaning: Odil, adolatlining, barhaqning bandasi (quli)

properties.name: Hibbatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni; Alloh ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Hidoy
properties.meaning: Qar. Hidoyat

properties.name: Hidoyxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Hidoyatxo‘ja

properties.name: Hidoyat
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘lga boshlovchi, to‘gri yol topuvchi. Shakllari: Hidoyatbu, Hidoyatxon

properties.name: Hidoyatulla
properties.meaning: Alloh to‘g‘ri yo‘lga boshlovchi to‘gri yol korsatuvchidir yoki Alloh yoliga (togri yolga) boshlaydigan bola

properties.name: Hikmat
properties.meaning: Donolik, donishmandlik; mo‘jiza. Badanida qandaydir g‘ayritabiiy, ortiq belgi bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hikmatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning donoligi, donishmandligi yoki Allohning mo‘jizasi. Keyingi ma’noda ism badanida g‘ayritabiiy nuqson yoki ortiqcha belgi bilan tug‘ilgan bolalarga qo‘yiladi

properties.name: Hilvat
properties.meaning: o‘zini panaga oluvchi, yashiringan, maxfiy

properties.name: Hilla
properties.meaning: Ravo ko‘rilgan, kutilgan, istalgan bola

properties.name: Hiloliddin
properties.meaning: Dinning yangi, ko‘rkam oyi; dinning go‘zaligi, ko‘rki

properties.name: Hiloliy
properties.meaning: Yangi oydek, yangi oy monand go‘zal yoki yangi oy tuqqanda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Himmat
properties.meaning: Oliyjanob, saxovatli bola

properties.name: Himmatali
properties.meaning: Alining muruvvati, saxovati bo‘lgan bola; Alining tuhfasi, ehsoni

properties.name: Himmatqul
properties.meaning: Allohning olijanob, saxovatli bandasi

properties.name: Himoyiddin
properties.meaning: Qar. Humoyiddin

properties.name: Hindboy, Hindiboy
properties.meaning: Yovvosh, beozor, muloyim, mo‘min-qobil bola yoki qora bola

properties.name: Hinduboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Hindboy

properties.name: Hisom
properties.meaning: Qilich, shamshir, tig‘. Asli: Hisomiddin (qar.). Shakllari: Hisomboy, Hisomxo‘ja

properties.name: Hisomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning qilichi, shamshiri yoki dinning qilichdek o‘tkir bolasi

properties.name: Hisor, Hisorboy
properties.meaning: Qo‘rg‘on, qal’a, istehkomdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Hifziddin
properties.meaning: Dinni asrovchi; din muhofazakori

properties.name: Hodi, Hodiy
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘l ko‘rsatuvchi, togri yolga boshlovchi; yetakchi, yolboshchi; pir, rahnamo, murshid. Bu nom Allohi Taoloning va Muhammad (sav)ning sifatlaridan biridir. Shakllari: Hodiboy, Hodixon, Hodixoja, Hodiqul

properties.name: Hodimat
properties.meaning: Qar. Hodimuhammad

properties.name: Hodimirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Hodi va Mirza

properties.name: Hodimuhammad
properties.meaning: Muhammad (sav) to‘g‘ri yo‘lga, islom yo‘liga boshlovchidir

properties.name: Hodixon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hodi (Hodi+xon)

properties.name: Hodixo‘ja
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘l, hidoyat yo‘lini korsatuvchi avliyozoda, aslzoda

properties.name: Hodiya
properties.meaning: Qar. Hodi (Hodi+ya)

properties.name: Hodiqul
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘lga boshlovchining, ya’ni Allohning bandasi

properties.name: Hodiqurbon
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan to‘g‘ri yo‘ldan, din yolidan boradigan bola yoki Allohning qurboni oyida tugilgan bandasi

properties.name: Hoji
properties.meaning: Ziyoratchi, sig‘inuvchi Ka’bani (Makkada) ziyorat qilgan shaxs. Shakllari: Hojibek, Hojibibi, Hojibeka, Hojiboy, Hojixon

properties.name: Hojiakbar
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Akbar

properties.name: Hojiali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Ali

properties.name: Hojiahmad
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Ahmad

properties.name: Hojib
properties.meaning: Darvozabon, eshil qoravuli yoki to‘silgan, pardali

properties.name: Hojibola
properties.meaning: Hojilar avlodiga mansub bola, hoji farzandi

properties.name: Hojibotir
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Botir

properties.name: Hojiboqi
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Boqi

properties.name: Hojibulla
properties.meaning: Alloh yo‘liga boshlovchi, islomga bo‘ysunuvchi, xudojo‘y

properties.name: Hojiburhon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Burhon

properties.name: Hojivali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Vali

properties.name: Hojidada
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Dada yoki hoji dadasining ismini olgan bola

properties.name: Hojiddin
properties.meaning: Din yo‘lida ziyorat qiluvchi, hoji

properties.name: Hojiislom
properties.meaning: Islom dini ziyoratchisi yoki qar. Hoji va Islom

properties.name: Hojikamol
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Kamol

properties.name: Hojikarim
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Karim

properties.name: Hojikeldi
properties.meaning: Uyga hoji mehmon bo‘lib kelganda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hojim
properties.meaning: Hojimurod, Hojimuhammad kabi ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Hojimamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Hojimuhammad

properties.name: Hojimat
properties.meaning: Qar. Hojimuhammad

properties.name: Hojimirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Mirza

properties.name: Hojimurod
properties.meaning: Hoji yetkazgan orzu, maqsad; hoji ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Hojimuhammad
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Muhammad

properties.name: Hojimuhiddin
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Muhiddin

properties.name: Hojin
properties.meaning: Hojinazar, Hojiniyoz kabi ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Hojinabi
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Nabi

properties.name: Hojinazar
properties.meaning: Hojining nafasi, iltifoti (nazar-e’tibori) tufayli tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hojinafas
properties.meaning: Hojining mo‘jifasi, nafasi tufayli tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hojiniyoz
properties.meaning: Hojidan o‘tinib so‘rab olingan bola yoki hojining tuhfasi, ehsoni

properties.name: Hojiniso
properties.meaning: Ziyotachi, xudojo‘y ayol yoki hojilar oilasiga mansub qiz

properties.name: Hojiomon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Omon yoki hojilar oilasiga mansub o‘g‘il, sog‘-omon ulg‘aysin

properties.name: Hojipo‘lat
properties.meaning: Hojilar oilasiga mansub, po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Hojirahim
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahim

properties.name: Hojirahmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahmat

properties.name: Hojirahmon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahmon

properties.name: Hojisalim
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Salim

properties.name: Hojisafar
properties.meaning: Hojilar oilasiga mansub va safar oyida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hojisafo
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Safo

properties.name: Hojisiddiq
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Siddiq

properties.name: Hojisoli
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Soli(h)

properties.name: Hojiturdi
properties.meaning: Hojilar oilasiga mansub bola turadi, yashaydi

properties.name: Hojiumar
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Umar

properties.name: Hojiusmon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Usmon

properties.name: Hojixol
properties.meaning: Hojilar oilasiga mansub va badanida xol bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Hojixon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji (Hoji+xon)

properties.name: Hojixo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar, aslzodalar oilasiga mansub bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Hojio‘roz
properties.meaning: Hojilar, oqsuyaklar oilasiga mansub baxtli bola

properties.name: Hojiqobil
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qobil

properties.name: Hojiqori
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qori

properties.name: Hojiqosim
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qosim

properties.name: Hojiqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji (Hoji+qul)

properties.name: Hojiqurbon
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan va hojilar oilasiga mansub bola

properties.name: Hojiqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qo‘zi

properties.name: Hozir
properties.meaning: Himoyalanan, muhofazalangan, xavfdan xoli. Shakllari: Hozirbek, Hozirboy, Hozirqul

properties.name: Hoziq
properties.meaning: Mohir, bilimdon, o‘z hunarini ustasi yoki itoatkor, yovvosh

properties.name: Hokim
properties.meaning: Boshliq, hukmdor, yo‘lboshchi. Eht.: Hakim (qar.)

properties.name: Homid
properties.meaning: Shukur qiluvchi, qanoat qiluvchi, sabr-toqatli. Shakllari: Homidjon, Homidboy, Homidxon

properties.name: Homidali
properties.meaning: Qar. Homid va Ali

properties.name: Homiddin
properties.meaning: Dinga shukronalar aytuvchi, dindan minnat bo‘luvchi, dinga sig‘inuvchi bola

properties.name: Homidxon
properties.meaning: Shukuronalar aytuvchi, sabr-qanoatli hamda martabali bola

properties.name: Homil
properties.meaning: Aynan: Ko‘tarib yuruvchi, eltuvchi yoki homul-taxtiravon; taxtiravonni ko‘tarib yuradigan

properties.name: Horun
properties.meaning: Aynan: Aaron - tog‘lik, o‘jar, qaytmas, yohud boy, badavlat yoki posbon, qorovul, qo‘riqchi. Bibliya dagi Aaron ismining arabcha shakli. Bu nom Muso payg‘ambarning katta akasi ismi ham bolgan

properties.name: Hosil
properties.meaning: Meva, samara, natija; farzand yoki aniq, ravshan. Shakllari: Hosiljon, Hosiloy

properties.name: Hosilmurod
properties.meaning: Erishilgan, ushalgan orzu, maqsad

properties.name: Hosilot
properties.meaning: Unum, hosil, samara yoki ulg‘ayib hosilot (amal) raisi bo‘lsin, amaldor bo‘lsin

properties.name: Hosiltosh
properties.meaning: Orzuimiz mevasi bo‘lgan bola toshdek mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Hotam
properties.meaning: Saxiy, qo‘li ochiq, oliyhimmat. Asli bu ism saxiyligi bilan juda mashhur bo‘lgan Hotami Toy arabning homidandir yoki hotam - yo‘lboshchi, boshliq. Shakllari: Hotamxo‘ja, Hotamsho, Hotamqul

properties.name: Hotamtoy
properties.meaning: o‘ta saxiy, qo‘li ochiq. Hotam Toy nomli o‘ta saxiyligi bilan mashhur bo‘lgan arabning ismi

properties.name: Hotamxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hotam (Hotam+xon)

properties.name: Hotamxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar, aslzodalar naslidan bo‘lgan saxiy, jo‘mard bola

properties.name: Hotamsho
properties.meaning: Qar. Hotam va Sho(h)

properties.name: Hotamqul
properties.meaning: Allohning saxiy, jo‘mard bandasi

properties.name: Hotif
properties.meaning: g‘oyibdan ovoz beruvchi, chaqiruvchi. Sol: Xotif

properties.name: Hofiz
properties.meaning: o‘z panohida saqlovchi, asrovchi, mana shu ma’noda bu nom Allohning sifatlaridan biridir. Qar. Abduhofiz, shuningdek hofiz Quronni yoddan o‘quvchi, qiroatchi yoki ashulasi, quychi

properties.name: Hofizxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hofiz (Hofiz+xon)

properties.name: Hoshim
properties.meaning: Maydalovchi, ushatuvchi; nonni ushatuvchi, taqsimlovchi yoki hurmatli, hurmatga sazovor. Bu nom Muhammad (sav) ning katta o‘g‘li ismi bo‘lgan. Shakllari: Hoshimbek, Hoshimjon, Hoshimxon

properties.name: Hoshimali
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoshim va Ali

properties.name: Hoshimxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Hoshim va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Hoshirboy
properties.meaning: Hoshir - to‘plovchi, hamlovchi; uyushtiruvchi. Eht.: Hoshirboy, Ashirboy, Ashurboy (qar.)

properties.name: Hubbim
properties.meaning: Hub so‘zi boshlangan ismlarning eq.shakli. (Hubbiniso, Hubbishtosh) yoki suyukli, azizam

properties.name: Hubbimjon
properties.meaning: Qar. Hubbim (Hubbim+jon)

properties.name: Hubbimtosh
properties.meaning: Suyukli, aziz bola toshdek mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Huvaydo
properties.meaning: Belgili, oshkoro; ravshan, aniq

properties.name: Hujjat
properties.meaning: Qar. Xujjatali

properties.name: Hujjatali
properties.meaning: Alining dalili, vakili (diniy masalalarda)

properties.name: Hujatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning dalili, vakili (diniy masalalarda)

properties.name: Huzur
properties.meaning: Osoyishtalik, osudalik; rohat, farog‘at. Shakllari: Huzurboy, Huzurjon, Huzurxon

properties.name: Hulkarboy
properties.meaning: Tolei Hulkar yulduzi kabi  yuksak bo‘lsin

properties.name: Humoyiddin
properties.meaning: Din ato qilgan baxt, saodat, davlat

properties.name: Humom
properties.meaning: Qavm (urug‘)ning boshlig‘I, dovyurak, jasur olam yoki qar. Humomiddin

properties.name: Humomiddin
properties.meaning: Din yo‘lboshchisi, peshvosi, rahnamosi

properties.name: Humoyun
properties.meaning: Qutlug‘, muborak, noyob, tengsiz

properties.name: Humoqul
properties.meaning: Allohning baxtli, davlatmand bandasi

properties.name: Hunar
properties.meaning: Kasb, mehnat, mahorat, mohirlik. Eht.: Unar (qar.). Shakllari: Hunarboy, Hunarjon, Hunarbu, Hunarxon

properties.name: Hurali
properties.meaning: Baxtli, erkin, ozod bo‘lib o‘ssin va Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Hurbatulla
properties.meaning: Hurmatulla ismining o‘zgargan shakli bo‘lishi mumkin

properties.name: Hurboy
properties.meaning: Erkin, ozod, xurram bola

properties.name: Hurvali
properties.meaning: Allohga yaqin turuvchi, baxtli bola

properties.name: Hurzamon
properties.meaning: Davrining ozod, baxtiyor o‘g‘li

properties.name: Hurli
properties.meaning: Ozod, erkin yoki go‘zal, chiroyli

properties.name: Hurliboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Hurli

properties.name: Hurmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Hurmuhammad

properties.name: Hurmat
properties.meaning: Qadrli, izzatli, e’zoz ehtiromga sazovor bola yoki qar. Hurmuhammad

properties.name: Hurmatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning e’zozi, hurmati, qadri yoki Allohning hurmatiga sazovor bola

properties.name: Hurmatxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar, aslzodalar naslidan bo‘lgan e’zozli bola

properties.name: Hurulla
properties.meaning: Allohning go‘zal, erkin, baxtiyor bolasi

properties.name: Hurqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qo‘zi kabi o‘ynoqlab, erkin, quvnoq bo‘lib o‘ssin

properties.name: Husayn
properties.meaning: Hasan (qar.) ismning eq.shakli bo‘lib yaxshi, mehribon, saxiy; chiroyli, go‘zal ma’nolarini anglatadi. Husayn ibn Ali (626-680) ismi bo‘lib, u Ali ibn Abu Tolingning Fotimadan tug‘ilgan ogli, Muhammad (sav)ning nabirasidir. Husayn uchinchi shia imomidir

properties.name: Husaynali
properties.meaning: Qar. Husayn va Ali

properties.name: Husaynmurod
properties.meaning: Husayn erishtirgan orzu yoki Husaynning tuhfasi, ehsoni

properties.name: Husaynniyoz
properties.meaning: Imom Husaynning tuhfasi, ehsoni yoki Husayndan o‘tinib so‘rab olingan bola

properties.name: Husaynqul
properties.meaning: Imom Husaynga xizmat qiluvchi, Husaynga sodiq bola

properties.name: Husan
properties.meaning: Qar. Husayn. Shakllari: Husanboy, Husanjon, Husanxon

properties.name: Husanali
properties.meaning: Qar. Husaynali

properties.name: Husancha
properties.meaning: Jajji, kenjatoy Husayn

properties.name: Husanqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Husaynqul

properties.name: Husanqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Husaynqo‘zi

properties.name: Husn
properties.meaning: Qar. Husniddin, Husnulla

properties.name: Husniddin
properties.meaning: Dinning chiroyi, ko‘rki yoki dinning go‘zal farzandi

properties.name: Husniyor
properties.meaning: Go‘zallikning, nafosatning yo‘ldoshi, ma’nosi; ko‘rkamlik yor bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Husnimardon

properties.name: Izoh
properties.meaning: Qar. Izohiddin

properties.name: Izohiddin
properties.meaning: Dinni sharhlovchi, tushuntiruvchi, talqin qiluvchi

properties.name: Izhor
properties.meaning: Qar. Izhoriddin

properties.name: Izhoriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning oshkoraligi; dinning namoyon va ravshanligi

properties.name: Iymanjon
properties.meaning: Iboli, uyatchan; odobli bola yoki kutib, intizor bo‘lib erishilgan bola

properties.name: Ikmol
properties.meaning: Kamolatga yetgan, mukammal bola

properties.name: Ikrom
properties.meaning: Izzat, ehtirom, obro‘, martaba yoki sovg‘a, tuhfa. Qar. Ikromiddin. Shakllari: Ikromjon, Ikromjon

properties.name: Ikromali
properties.meaning: Qar. Ikrom va Ali

properties.name: Ikromiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning yuksakligi, ulug‘vorligi, dinning mo‘tabarligi, e’zozli

properties.name: Ikrommirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Ikrom va Mirza

properties.name: Ikromxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan izzat-e’tiborga loyiq bola

properties.name: Ikromcha
properties.meaning: Izzatu e’zozli o‘g‘ilcha

properties.name: Ilash
properties.meaning: Otasiga (o‘zidan oldingi aka-opasiga) ergashib (ilashib) ulg‘aysin. Shakllari: Ilashboy, Ilashjon

properties.name: Ilashqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilash (Ilash+qul)

properties.name: Ildam
properties.meaning: Chaqqon, g‘ayratli bola

properties.name: Ildiz
properties.meaning: Ildizi mustahkam, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Ildirim
properties.meaning: Chaqmoq, yashun; nur, shu’la, yog‘du. Chaqqon chaqqanda tug‘ilgan bola. Sol: Yoldirim

properties.name: Ilyos
properties.meaning: Aynan: Mening tangrim Yeliyaxin (Yax’yo) Allohning kuchi, qudrati yoki xalqlarning sevimligi, kishilar qadrlovchi, ezozlovchi odam. Obihayot ichib Xizr kabi mangu tirik deb faraz qilinadigan payg‘ambarning nomi. Quruqda Xizr bo‘lsa, suvlikda Ilyos kishilarning madadkori, hamrohi deb hisoblanadi

properties.name: Ilyosali
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilyos va Ali

properties.name: Ilyosiddin
properties.meaning: Ilyosning dini, imoni, e’tiqodi

properties.name: Ilyosxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilyos

properties.name: Ilyosxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilyos (Ilyos+xo‘ja)

properties.name: Ilyosqul
properties.meaning: Ilyos payg‘ambarning quli, xizmatkori

properties.name: Ilim
properties.meaning: Ilimli, bilimdon. Sol: Ilimiddin. Shakllari: Ilimbek, Ilimboy, Ilimjon

properties.name: Ilimbek
properties.meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan, bilimli, dono bola

properties.name: Ilimdor
properties.meaning: Bilimdon, donishmand

properties.name: Ilkin
properties.meaning: To‘ng‘ich bola yoki el farzandi

properties.name: Ilmi
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilmiddin

properties.name: Ilmiddin
properties.meaning: Din ilmi, diniy ma’rifat; din ilmi bilimdoni

properties.name: Ilmiyor
properties.meaning: Bilimli, o‘qimishli, ilmu ma’rifat yor bo‘lsin

properties.name: Ilmijon
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilmi (Ilmi+jon)

properties.name: Ilmirahim
properties.meaning: Allohning ilmi; rahm-shafqat, muruvvat ilmi

properties.name: Ilmirahmon
properties.meaning: Rahmonning (qar.), ya’ni Alloh ilmi; mehru shafqat, muruvvat ilmi

properties.name: Ilmiyazdon
properties.meaning: Alloh ilmi; Allohning kuchi, qudrati, mo‘jizasi

properties.name: Ilmiyat
properties.meaning: Bilimlar sohibi, ma’rifatli, dono

properties.name: Ilmihayot
properties.meaning: Hayot, tiriklik ilmi; baxtu saodat ilmi

properties.name: ilmulla
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilimulla

properties.name: Ilojboy
properties.meaning: Da’vo, shifo. Asli: Ilojiddin

properties.name: Ilojiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning ko‘magi, yordami; dinning xaloskorligi

properties.name: Ilohbaxsh
properties.meaning: Allohga baxsh etgan, ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Ilohdod
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan, Alloh tuhfa qilgan bola

properties.name: Ilohyor
properties.meaning: Alloh qo‘llovchi, panohiga oluvchi bola

properties.name: Ilg‘or
properties.meaning: Oldinga boruvchi, yetakchi; tezkor, ildam yoki va’da, ahdu paymon

properties.name: Ilhom
properties.meaning: Ruhlanish, jo‘sh urish; intilish, hayoti sevish

properties.name: Ilhomali
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilhom va Ali

properties.name: Ilhomiddin
properties.meaning: Dindan ruhlanuvchi, ilhomlanuvchi

properties.name: Ilhommirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilhom va Mirza

properties.name: Ilhomxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan ruhlanib, g‘ayrati jo‘sh urib yuruvchi bola

properties.name: Imdod
properties.meaning: Ko‘mak, madad, yordam. Qar. Imdodulla

properties.name: Imdodulla
properties.meaning: Allohning ko‘magi, yordami, marhamati

properties.name: Imin
properties.meaning: Xavfsiz, bexatar. Qar. Emin. Shakllari: Iminjon, Imintoy, Imincha

properties.name: Imod, Imonboy
properties.meaning: Tayanch, suyanchiq, turgak, madad, yordam

properties.name: Imodali
properties.meaning: Ali ato qilgan suyanch, madad; Alining ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan bola

properties.name: Imodiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning tayanchi, asosi yoki dinning bosh homiysi, dinning sodiq xizmatkori

properties.name: Imodulla
properties.meaning: Allohning ko‘magi, iltifoti yoki Alloh ato qilgan tayanch, suyanch

properties.name: Imon
properties.meaning: Aynan: Oldinda turuvchi, peshvo; masjidda oldinda turib namozni boshqaruvchi; musulmonlarning diniy rahbari, peshvosi. Imom so‘zi Alining avlodlari hisoblanuvchi va shiitlar mazhabiga mansub kishilarning VII-X asrlardan udum bo‘lib kelgan unvonidir va u ushbu unvonga sazovor shaxsning ismiga qo‘shib aytilgan: Imom ALi kabi

properties.name: Imomali
properties.meaning: Ali oldinda turuvchi, rahbar, peshvodir. Muhammad (sav)ning tog‘asi shiitlarning birinchi imomi hisoblanadi. Shu sababli u Imomali deb yuritilgan va bu nom kishilar ismiga ham o‘tgan

properties.name: Imombaxsh
properties.meaning: Imom ato qilgan, bergan bola

properties.name: Imombek
properties.meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan diniy peshvo, diniy rahbar

properties.name: Imombergan
properties.meaning: Diniy boshliq (peshvo) ato qilgan, erishtirgan bola. Bu ism biror muqaddas qadamjoyga ziyorat qilingach tug‘ilgan bolaga beriladi

properties.name: Imomberdi
properties.meaning: Diniy peshvo, muqaddas avliyo ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Imomboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Imom (Imom+boy)

properties.name: Imomyor
properties.meaning: Imom (diniy peshvoning) do‘sti, hamrohi, yo‘ldoshi yoki imom hamroh, yo‘ldosh bo‘luvchi, panohiga oluvchi bola

properties.name: Imomzoda
properties.meaning: Imomning farzandi, o‘g‘li yoki imomlar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Imomiddin
properties.meaning: Din boshlig‘I, din homiysi; din peshvosi; dinning sodiq xizmatkori

properties.name: Imommirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Imom va Mirza

properties.name: Imommurod
properties.meaning: Imom ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan orzu yoki imom ato qilgan bola ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Imommuhammad
properties.meaning: Muhammad (sav) dinning peshvosi, sardoridir

properties.name: Imomnazar
properties.meaning: Din peshvosining marhamati, iltifoti tufayli erishilgan bola; imomning ehsoni, tuhfasi

properties.name: Imomnafas
properties.meaning: Imomning qudrati (nafasi) tegib erishilgan bola

properties.name: Imomniyoz
properties.meaning: Imomdan o‘tinib, tilab, olingan bola yoki imom bergan tuhfa, ehson

properties.name: Imomrasul
properties.meaning: Qar. Imom va Rasul

properties.name: Imomsaid
properties.meaning: Imom erishtirgan baxtli, tolei baland bola

properties.name: Imomxol
properties.meaning: Dinning xolli peshvosi, boshlig‘i

properties.name: Imomxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan din peshvosi

properties.name: Imomcha
properties.meaning: Madrasa talabasi, kelgusida imom bo‘luvchi bola yoki imomlarning kichigi, kenjasi

properties.name: Imomqul
properties.meaning: Din peshvosi (imom)ning quli, imomga sodiq bola

properties.name: Imom
properties.meaning: Ishonch, e’tiqod, ishonish, sig‘inish. Imom Islom dinining asosiy shartlaridan biri bo‘lib, bunda Allohga, islom dini va Muhammadga ishonch, etiqod ko‘zda tutiladi. Demak, imon, etiqodli bola. Shakllari: Imonbek, Imonboy, Imonjon

properties.name: Imonali
properties.meaning: Aliga e’tiqod qiluvchi, sig‘inuvchi bola yoki imon-etiqodli bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Imonberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan imon-e’tiqodli bola

properties.name: Imonkeldi
properties.meaning: Imon-e’tiqodli tilladek aziz, bebaho bola

properties.name: Imontilla
properties.meaning: Dinga e’tiqodli tilladek aziz, bebaho bola

properties.name: Imonqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Imon (Imon+qul)

properties.name: Imron
properties.meaning: Tiriklik, barhayotlik, uzoq umr ko‘ruvchi

properties.name: Imroh
properties.meaning: Do‘stlik, birodarlik, o‘rtoqlik

properties.name: Imtiyoz
properties.meaning: o‘zgalardan sarbaland, farqli (imtiyozli) qilib berilgan bola

properties.name: Imyamin
properties.meaning: Qar. Ibniyamin

properties.name: Inar
properties.meaning: Inar (tuyaning bir xol zoti) kabi kuchli, qudratli bola

properties.name: Inarkeldi
properties.meaning: Inar (qar.) dek kuchli, baquvvat bola tug‘ildo

properties.name: Inimcha
properties.meaning: Ukacha, inicha; oldingi bolalarga ukacha bo‘lib yursin

properties.name: Inkor
properties.meaning: Tavqa qiluvchi, Allohi taolo yo‘liga o‘tuvchi bola. Shakli: Inkorbek, Inkorboy

properties.name: Inob
properties.meaning: Inobat, Inobiddin (qar.) ismlarining eq.shakllari: Inobboy, Inobjon, Inobxon

properties.name: Inobiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning marhamati, himmati, inobati

properties.name: Inod
properties.meaning: o‘jar, qaytmas, sarkash bola

properties.name: Inol
properties.meaning: Hokim, hukmron, podshoh yoki yalinib, yolg‘orib erishilgan bola

properties.name: Inon, Inonjon
properties.meaning: Umid qilish, ishonish, inonish, ya’ni bola yashab ketadi deb umid qilinadi

properties.name: Inonch
properties.meaning: Ishonish, umidlanish, ya’ni bolaning yashab ketishiga umid bog‘lash

properties.name: Inoyat
properties.meaning: Xayrixohlik, ko‘mak, ehson, iltifot. Asli: Inoyatulla (qar.)

properties.name: Inoyatali
properties.meaning: Alining himmati, ehsoni, ko‘magi

properties.name: Inoyatrasul
properties.meaning: Payg‘ambarning lutfu karami, ko‘magi bilan erishilgan bola

properties.name: Inoyatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning marhamati, lutfu karami yoki Allohning fikri, yodi. Ushbu nom Muhammad (sav)ning sifati (laqab)laridan biri bo‘lgan

properties.name: Inoyatqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Inoyat (Inoyat+qul)

properties.name: Inoq
properties.meaning: Do‘st, o‘rtoq, yo‘ldosh yoki o‘ziga mustaqil bolgan shaxs. Buxoro xonligida eng yuqori mansablardan biri ham inoq deb yuritiladi

properties.name: Inoqmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Inoq va Mirza

properties.name: Inog‘om
properties.meaning: In’om, sovg‘a, tuhfa, hadya

properties.name: Inson
properties.meaning: Odam, kishi; odamshavanda bola

properties.name: Insof, Insofboy
properties.meaning: Pokiza, adolatli. Shakllari: Insofboy, Insofjon

properties.name: Insofali
properties.meaning: Pokiza, adolatpesha bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Insofiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning insofli, sabr-qanoatli farzandi

properties.name: Intizom
properties.meaning: Tartibli, sarishta, odobli

properties.name: Intizor
properties.meaning: Intiq bo‘lib, orziqib kutilgan

properties.name: Intiq, Intiqjon
properties.meaning: Orziqib, intiq bo‘lib kutilgan

properties.name: Intiqom
properties.meaning: Oldingi vafot etrgan farzandlar evaziga berilgan bola

properties.name: In’om
properties.meaning: Tuhfa, tortiq qilib berilgan. Shakllari: In’omboy, Inomjon

properties.name: In’omali
properties.meaning: Alining sovg‘asi, tuhfasi

properties.name: In’omiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning tuhfasi, sovg‘asi; tortig‘i

properties.name: In’ommirza
properties.meaning: Qar. In’om va Mirza

properties.name: In’omulla
properties.meaning: Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni

properties.name: In’ommuhammad
properties.meaning: Muhammad (sav)ning tuhfasi, ehsoni, marhamati

properties.name: In’omnazar
properties.meaning: Alloh e’tibor, muruvvat qilib bergan sovg‘a, ehson

properties.name: In’omto‘ra
properties.meaning: Alloh sovg‘a, tuhfa qilib bergan bola baland martabali bo‘lsin

properties.name: In’omxon
properties.meaning: Qar. In’om (Inom+xon)

properties.name: In’omqul
properties.meaning: Qar. In’om (Inom+qul)

properties.name: Inqilob
properties.meaning: Aynan: o‘zgarish, to‘ntarish. Inqilob farzandi. Yangi davrda paydo bo‘lgan ism

properties.name: Iris, Irisboy
properties.meaning: Iris- nasibali, farovon, baxtiyor yoki ota-onasining nasibasi, omadi bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Irisali
properties.meaning: Nasibali, rizq-ro‘zli, omadli bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Irisli
properties.meaning: Nasibali, baxtli bola. Sol: Iris

properties.name: Irismat
properties.meaning: Qar. Irismuhammad

properties.name: Irismurod
properties.meaning: Orzu qilingan nasibali bola yoki nasibasi butun bola ulg‘ayib murodu maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Iristoy
properties.meaning: Rizqu ro‘zli, nasibasi butun, omadli bola

properties.name: Irisxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan rizqu nasibasi butun bola

properties.name: Irisqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Iris (Iris+qul)

properties.name: Iroq, Iroqboy
properties.meaning: Aynan: Yiroq, ya’ni umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Irshod
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘l ko‘rsatuvchi, togri yolga undovchi boshliq, rahbar

properties.name: Iskandar
properties.meaning: Mard, qo‘rqmas, dovyurak, jasurlarning sardori yoki himoya qiluvchi, muhofazakor

properties.name: Iskandarbek
properties.meaning: Beklar avlodidan bo‘lgan bola. Iskandar (qar.)dek jasur bo‘lsin

properties.name: Iskandarsho
properties.meaning: Iskandar shohdek jasur, dovyurak

properties.name: Iskandarqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Iskandar (Iskandar+qul)

properties.name: Islimiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning bezagi, ko‘rki yoki dinga rivoj beruvchi, yuksaltiruvchi

properties.name: Islom
properties.meaning: Aynan: O‘zini Allohning ixtiyoriga topshirish itoatkor, islomga bo‘ysungan. Musulmonlar, Muhammad (sav) dinining nomi. Shakllari: Islomboy, Islombek, Islomjon

properties.name: Islomali
properties.meaning: Islomga itoat qiluvchi, musulmon bola Ali o‘z panohida olsin

properties.name: Islombek
properties.meaning: Beklar avlodidan bo‘lgan, musulmonlar diniga bo‘ysungan bola

properties.name: Islomberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh ato qilgan musulmon bola yoki Alloh musulmon bola ato qildi

properties.name: Islomboqi
properties.meaning: Musulmonlar dini (islom) abadiy, boqiydir yoki Muhammad diniga itoat qiluvchi bolaning umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Islomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinga sodiq bola, xudojo‘y, zohid

properties.name: Islommirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Islom va Mirza

properties.name: Islommurod
properties.meaning: Islom erishtirgan orzu, murod yoki Allohga bo‘ysungan bola ulg‘ayib murodiga yetsin

properties.name: Islomnur
properties.meaning: Musulmonlar dini (islom)ning nuri, yog‘dusi; islom ato qilgan baxt, omad

properties.name: Islomxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Islom(Islom+xon)

properties.name: Islomxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan musulmon bola

properties.name: Islomsho
properties.meaning: Qar. Islom va Sho(h)

properties.name: Islomqul
properties.meaning: Islomning sodiq xizmatkori, quli

properties.name: Islomg‘ozi
properties.meaning: Islom yo‘lida kurashuvchi va g‘olib chiquvchi bola

properties.name: Islomhoji
properties.meaning: Qar. Islom va Hoji yoki Ka’bani ziyorat qilgan musulmon

properties.name: Islohot
properties.meaning: o‘zgarishm tuzatish (islohot) yillari tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Isman
properties.meaning: Ismatulla ismining qisqargan shakli. Eht.: Isfan

properties.name: Ismanali
properties.meaning: Qar. Isman va Ali yoki Isfanali

properties.name: Ismandiyor
properties.meaning: Qar. Isfandiyor

properties.name: Ismanjon
properties.meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+jon) yoki Ismatulla

properties.name: Istamtoy
properties.meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+toy) yoki Ismatulla

properties.name: Ismonxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+xo‘ja) yoki Ismatulla

properties.name: Ismancha
properties.meaning: Kenja, jajji. Isfan (qar.) yoki Ismatulla

properties.name: Ismanqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Isman (Isman+qul) yoki Ismatulla

properties.name: Ismat
properties.meaning: Pokiza, ozoda, gunohsiz; taqvodor, poro. Shakllari: Ismatjon, Ismatxon

properties.name: Ismatyor
properties.meaning: Soflik, pokizalik; yaxshi fazilatlar hamdami

properties.name: Ismatmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Ismat va Mirza

properties.name: Ismatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning begunoh, pokiza, yaxshi xislatlar sohibi bo‘lmish bandasi. Bu nom Muhammad (sav)ning sifati (laqabi) bo‘lgan

properties.name: Ismatqul
properties.meaning: Pokiza, begunoh bola. Qar. Ismat (Ismat+qul)

properties.name: Ismoil
properties.meaning: Aynan: Xudo eshitdi yoki Allohdan so‘rab olingan, Alloh tuhfa qilgan bola. Tavrotdagi rivoyatga ko‘ra, Ibrohim payg‘ambarning xotini Hojar Allohdan farzand so‘rab ijtijo qilgan. Shu tufayli tugilgan bolaga Ishmael (Ismoil) deb ism berishgan. Bu nom MUhammad (sav) oglining ismi ham bolgan. Shakllari: Ismoiljon, Ismoilxon

properties.name: Ismoilxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Ismoil va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Ismoilsho
properties.meaning: Qar. Ismoil va Sho(h)

properties.name: Ismoilqul
properties.meaning: Ismoilning quli, Ismoilga bo‘ysunuvchi

properties.name: Iso
properties.meaning: Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni; lutfu karami; Allohning ko‘magi yoki Allohning yaqini. Iso-qadimiy yahudiycha Jexogua, Iisus (Xristos) nomining arabcha shaklidir

properties.name: Isoboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Iso (Iso+boy)

properties.name: Isoyor
properties.meaning: Iso (payg‘ambar) o‘z panohiga oluvchi, qo‘llovchi bola

properties.name: Isom
properties.meaning: Tayanch, suyanch, ya’ni ota-onasiga suyanchiq, ko‘makchi bo‘luvchi bola

properties.name: Isomamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Isomuhammad

properties.name: Isomat
properties.meaning: Qar. Isomuhammad

properties.name: Isomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning tutqichi, suyanchi; dinga madad beruvchi, ko‘makdosh

properties.name: Isomurod
properties.meaning: Iso yetkazgan orzu, tilak, Isoning muruvvati, tuhfasi

properties.name: Isomuhammad
properties.meaning: Qar. Iso va Muhammad

properties.name: Isomxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Isom (Islom+xon)

properties.name: Isomxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Ota-onasining suyanchig‘i, madadkori bo‘lgan, xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Isonafas
properties.meaning: Iso (payg‘ambar)ning nafasi, ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan bola yoki Iso nafasli; zukko, zehnli bola

properties.name: Isotilla
properties.meaning: Qar. Iso va Tilla

properties.name: Isotoy
properties.meaning: Iso payg‘ambar ismi berilgan aziz, suyukli bola yoki qar. Iso (Iso+toy)

properties.name: Isoxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Iso (Iso+xon)

properties.name: Isoxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Iso payg‘ambar nomi berilgan va xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Isoq
properties.meaning: Qar. Is’hoq. Shakllari: Isoqjon, Isoqboy

properties.name: Isoqali
properties.meaning: Qar. Is’hoq va Ali

properties.name: Isoqul
properties.meaning: Iso (as)ning quli

properties.name: Ispan
properties.meaning: Ismand  -  Isfand - isiriq, hazratispand. Xalq bu o‘simlim, uning hidi kishini balo-qazodan, ko‘z tegishdan arraydi deb hisoblaydi. Shu tufayli uning chaqaloqqa ism sifatida qo‘yiladi

properties.name: Isroil
properties.meaning: Alloh yo‘lida kurashuvchi

properties.name: Isrofil
properties.meaning: Aynan: :Xudoning xizmatkori, Allohning hukmini ado etuvchi: Qadimiy yahudiycha Saraf ismining arabcha shakli. Rivoyatga ko‘ra, u qiyomat kuni nay chalib o‘liklarni tiriltirib bir yerga to‘playdigan, odamlarni ogohlantiradigan farsihtadir. Ba’zi manbalarda yondiruvchi, alangalantiruvchi deb izohlanadi

properties.name: Istad
properties.meaning: Tursun, yashasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Istak, Istakboy
properties.meaning: Xohlab, iltijolar qilib olingan bola

properties.name: Istakgul
properties.meaning: Xohlangan, orzu qilingan va guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Istamas
properties.meaning: Chaqaloqni dushmani bo‘lmish yovuz kuchlar bolani istamaydi, mensimaydi, ko‘zga ilmaydi, demak bola sog‘u omon bo‘ladi deyilgan ma’noda. Sol: Itolmas, Itemas

properties.name: Istamboqi
properties.meaning: Boqiy turuvchi, umri uzoq bo‘luvchi bola

properties.name: Istamqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Istam (Istam+qul)

properties.name: Istatpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Tursin, yashasin va po‘latdek mahkam, mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Istatulla
properties.meaning: Alloh ato qilgan bola tursin, yashasin yoki Alloh umrini uzoq qilib bergan bola

properties.name: Iste’dod
properties.meaning: Qobiliyatli, epchil, uddaburon

properties.name: Isfan
properties.meaning: Muqaddas, ya’ni Alloh. Asli: Isfandiyor (qar.)

properties.name: Isfandiyor
properties.meaning: Muqaddasning, ya’ni Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni, muqadda tuhfa. Qadimgi Eron dostonlarida tasvirlangan, o‘z dushmanlariga tutqich bermaydigan qahramonlardan birining nomi. Sol: Asfandiyor (qar.)

properties.name: Isfahon
properties.meaning: Isfahon (qilich)dek keskir va mahkam. Bu Eronning mashhur shahzodalaridan birining nomi hamdir

properties.name: Is’hoq, Is’hoqjon
properties.meaning: Aynan: Kulgi, xandon, kuluvchi, kulayotgan. Is’hoq payg‘ambarning ham ismidir

properties.name: Is’hoqali
properties.meaning: Qar. Is’hoq va ALi

properties.name: Is’hoqnazar
properties.meaning: Is’hoq payg‘ambarning marhamatli, iltifoti, nazar qilishi tufayli erishilgan o‘g‘il; Ishoq payg‘ambarning nazari, mehri tushgan bola

properties.name: Is’hoqto‘ra
properties.meaning: Qar. Is’hoq va To‘ra

properties.name: Is’hoqxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Is’hoq payg‘ambar ismi berilgan xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Is’hoqqul
properties.meaning: Is’hoq (as)ning quli, sodiq xizmatkori

properties.name: Itboy
properties.meaning: Idek arzimas bola. Bu ism chaqaloqqa u yomon ko‘zlardan uzoq bo‘lsin, unga ko‘z tegmasin deb beriladi

properties.name: Itemas
properties.meaning: Bu bolani tashlasang, it ham emaydi, u shunchalik yomon jirkanch degan man’noda beriluvchi ism. Bu bilan chaqaloqni o‘limdan asrash ko‘zga tutiladi

properties.name: Ijton
properties.meaning: Idek arzimas bola. Bu ko‘z tegmasin degan ma’noga qo‘yiladi

properties.name: Itolmas
properties.meaning: Bu bolani hattoki it ham olmaydi, uning hech kimga keragi yo‘q, deyilagan ma’noga qo‘yiladi. Bu bilan bolani ko‘z tegishdan, bevaqt o‘limdan asramoqchi bolishadi

properties.name: Ittifoq
properties.meaning: Oldingi farzandlarga qo‘shilib ketsin va ittidoq bo‘lib yashasin

properties.name: Iftixor
properties.meaning: Faxr, g‘urur; shonu shavkat, ulg‘ayib elining g‘ururi, iftixori bo‘lsin

properties.name: Iftixoriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning ulug‘vorligi, shonu sharafi, shuhrati yoki dinning iftixori

properties.name: Iffatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning odobli, pokdomon bandasi

properties.name: Ixlos
properties.meaning: Smimiy, sofdil, sadoqatli bola. Shakllari: Ixlosboy, Ixlosjon

properties.name: Ixlosiddin
properties.meaning: Dinga ixlos qo‘ygan, dinga sadoqatli bola

properties.name: Ixlosxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan sofdil, sadoqatli bola

properties.name: Ixtiyor
properties.meaning: Erki o‘zida, ozod, hur bola

properties.name: Ixtiyoriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning saralangan kishisi, dinning mumtoz farzandi yoki dinning irodasi, xohishi

properties.name: Ixtiyorxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan erkli, ozod bola

properties.name: Ixshid
properties.meaning: Hokim, amir; sulton, shoh; hukmron

properties.name: Ishiq
properties.meaning: Shu’la, yog‘du, ravshanlik, yorug‘lik

properties.name: Ishrat
properties.meaning: Lazzat, quvnoqlik; baxtiyor, shodon

properties.name: Ishratxon
properties.meaning: Shodlik, quvnoqlik, baxtiyorlik

properties.name: Ishchanboy
properties.meaning: Mehnatkash, g‘ayratli. Eht.: Eshjonboy (qar.)

properties.name: Iqbol
properties.meaning: Baxt, saodat; omad, porloq kelajak. Shakllari: Iqboloy, Iqbolxon

properties.name: Iqboliddin
properties.meaning: Dinning baxtu saodatli, kelajagi porloq farzandi yoki din bergan omadli, baxtli bola

properties.name: Iqbolmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Iqbol va Mirza

properties.name: Iqbolxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan baxtiyor, saodatmand bola

properties.name: Iqror
properties.meaning: Qar. Iqroriddin

properties.name: Iqroriddin
properties.meaning: Dinga bo‘ysungan, musulmonchilikni bo‘yniga olgan

properties.name: Ibo
properties.meaning: Andishali, uyat-iboli; odobli, ahloq qiz

properties.name: Ibobuvi
properties.meaning: Iboli, andishali, aqlli-xushli qiz

properties.name: Iboqul
properties.meaning: Ibo-andishali va guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Iboda
properties.meaning: Qul, cho‘ri qiz yoki qulning qizi. Ibod (Ibod+a)

properties.name: Ibodat
properties.meaning: Allohga sig‘inish, qulluq qilish, ya’ni Allohga sig‘inuvchi, xudojo‘y

properties.name: Iborat
properties.meaning: Xabar beruvchi; so‘zlovchi, notiqa

properties.name: Ibocha
properties.meaning: Uyatli, andishali, jajji, kenja qiz

properties.name: Idigul
properties.meaning: Hayit (bayram) kuni tug‘ilgan, guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Ijora
properties.meaning: Ijoz- mo‘jiza, karomat. Chaqaloqning badanida qandaydir ortiqcha belgilar bo‘lganida shunday ism beriladi. Sol: Karomat, Karomatulla

properties.name: Ijozat
properties.meaning: Mo‘mizalar, karomatlar. Qar. Ijoza yoki ato qilingan, nasib qilingan farzand

properties.name: Izbo‘ta
properties.meaning: Izzat-ikromli, shon-shuhratli bola

properties.name: Izzatbanot
properties.meaning: Qizlarning hurmatlisi, izzatlisi

properties.name: Izzatbeka
properties.meaning: Beklar nasliga mansub e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Izzatgul
properties.meaning: Qadr-qimmatli va guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Izzatjamol
properties.meaning: Izzatli, e’tiborli, zebo qiz

properties.name: Izzatjon
properties.meaning: Izzat-ehtiromga loyiq suyukli, shirin bola

properties.name: Izzatoy
properties.meaning: Qadrli, e’zozga sazovor bo‘lgan oydek suluv qiz

properties.name: Izzatxon
properties.meaning: Izzat-ikromga sazovor baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Izolat
properties.meaning: Himoya qilingan; mahkam, mustahkam

properties.name: Izora
properties.meaning: Qo‘rg‘oshin, qo‘rg‘onshindek mahkam bola yoki shohi mato, romol kabi muloyim oyyuzli, gulchehra qiz

properties.name: Izofat
properties.meaning: Qo‘shilish, ko‘payish, ya’ni, oldingi bolalarga qo‘shilsin, ko‘payishsin

properties.name: Ikroma
properties.meaning: Izzat-ehtiromli, obro‘li qiz yoki Allohning muruvvati, tuhfasi

properties.name: Ikromlu
properties.meaning: Izzat-ikromli, baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Ikrombuvish
properties.meaning: Izzat-ehtiromga loyiq; qadrli qiz

properties.name: Ikromoy
properties.meaning: Izzat-e’tiborga loyiq va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Ikromxon
properties.meaning: Ehtiromga, izzatga sazovor, baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Ilashxon
properties.meaning: Onasiga o‘zidan oldingi aka-opalariga ilashib, ergashib yursin

properties.name: Ilimbeka
properties.meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan bilimli, dono qiz

properties.name: Ilich
properties.meaning: Yaylovda, o‘tloqda tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: ilmijamol
properties.meaning: Nafosat, go‘zal ilm sohibi

properties.name: Ilmijahon
properties.meaning: Dunyo bilimlarini egallagan; dono, donishmand qiz

properties.name: Ilmikamol
properties.meaning: Ilmda kamolatga yetgan, puxta bilimlar sohibi; donishmand

properties.name: Ilminiso
properties.meaning: Bilimli qiz; ayollarning bilimdoni, donosi

properties.name: Ilminoz
properties.meaning: Go‘zallik, nafosat, nazokat ilmi sohibasi

properties.name: Ilminoza
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilminoz (Ilminoz+a)

properties.name: Ilminur
properties.meaning: Ilm nuri, ilm ziyosi, ilm beruvchi, ilm baxsh etuvchi baxt

properties.name: Ilmisuluv
properties.meaning: Go‘zallik, nafosat ilmi

properties.name: Ilmiya
properties.meaning: Ilm sohibi, bilimli, ma’rifatli qiz

properties.name: Iloha
properties.meaning: Allohga baxsh etilgan qiz

properties.name: Ilohiy
properties.meaning: Xudojo‘y, taqvodor; sevimli, suyukli

properties.name: Iltijoxon
properties.meaning: o‘tinib, iltijo qilib erishilgan

properties.name: Iltimos
properties.meaning: Allohdan so‘rab olingan bola

properties.name: Iltifot
properties.meaning: Lutf, yaxshilik; mehru shafqat, marhamat

properties.name: Ilhoma
properties.meaning: Qar. Ilhon (Ilhom+a)

properties.name: Ilhomiya
properties.meaning: Ruhlanuvchi, ilhomlanuvchi yoki ilhom parisi

properties.name: Indira
properties.meaning: Indu - oy demakdir. Indira veda dinidagi iloha (xudo)lardan biri va u momaqaldiroq, yomg‘ir xudosi hisoblanadi

properties.name: Inja
properties.meaning: Zarif, nozik; nafis, odobli, nazokatli, xushmuomala qiz

properties.name: Injagul
properties.meaning: Nozik, zebo gul

properties.name: Inji
properties.meaning: Nozli, ishvali, nazokatli yoki tortiq, had’ya, inom

properties.name: Inju
properties.meaning: Marvarid, dur, javohir yoki xizmatchi, malay, cho‘ri

properties.name: Injubeka
properties.meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan durdek bebaho qiz yoki dur (marvariddek) bebaho ayol

properties.name: Inimchaxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Inimcha (Inimcha+xon)

properties.name: Inkoroy
properties.meaning: Allohga sig‘inuvchi, xudojo‘y, taqvodor ayol

properties.name: Inobat
properties.meaning: Alloh maqbul topib bergan bola; Allohning marhamati, himmati

properties.name: Inobxon
properties.meaning: Inobatxon (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

properties.name: Inoyatbibi
properties.meaning: Allohning ehsoni, marhami bo‘lgan baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Inoyatxol
properties.meaning: Allohning muruvvati, lutfu karami tufayli erishilgan xolli qiz

properties.name: In’oma
properties.meaning: Had’ya, sovg‘a qilib berilgan qiz

properties.name: Inqilobiya
properties.meaning: Inqilob, yangilanish qizi

properties.name: Ipak, Ipakxon
properties.meaning: Ipakdek muloyim, yoqimli qiz

properties.name: Ipakgul
properties.meaning: Ipak kabi muloyim va guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Ipaksuluv
properties.meaning: Ipakdek ko‘rkam, zebo qiz

properties.name: Ipakchi
properties.meaning: Ipak matolar to‘quvchi hunarmand, chevar qiz

properties.name: Iporgul
properties.meaning: Ipor guli (mushk)dek yoqimli qiz

properties.name: Irisa
properties.meaning: Iris- nasibali, baxtli qiz yoki ota-onasining nasibasi bo‘lgan qiz

properties.name: Irisbeka
properties.meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan rizq-ro‘zli, nasibasi butun qiz

properties.name: Irisbibi
properties.meaning: Rizq-nasibali qiz

properties.name: Irisbu, Irisbuvi
properties.meaning: Rizq-ro‘zli, nasibali qiz

properties.name: Irisdavlat
properties.meaning: Nasibasi butun va davlatmand qiz

properties.name: Irisjon
properties.meaning: Nasibasi butun va jondek aziz, shirin qiz

properties.name: Irisxol
properties.meaning: Rizqu ro‘zli, nasibali va xol bilan tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: Iroda
properties.meaning: Istab, orzu qilib erishilgan qiz yoki Allohning irodasi, muruvvati bo‘lgan qiz, yohud irodali chidamli qiz

properties.name: Irodat
properties.meaning: Tilab, orzu tilab olingan qiz yoki irodali, chidamli, sabru toqatli qiz

properties.name: Islomiya
properties.meaning: Allohga bo‘ysunuvchi, sig‘inuvchi qiz yoki islom dini muxlisi

properties.name: Ismigul
properties.meaning: Gul ismli qiz, nomi guldek zebo qiz

properties.name: Ismizar
properties.meaning: Tillo (yaxshi) ism sohibi, eng go‘zal ismli qiz

properties.name: Isminoz
properties.meaning: Nozik va nafis ismli qiz

properties.name: Isobat
properties.meaning: To‘g‘rilik, rostlik, adolat sohibasi

properties.name: Isoberdi
properties.meaning: Iso (payg‘ambar) bergan, ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Isolat
properties.meaning: Mahkam, mustahkam, umri uzoq qiz

properties.name: Istadoy
properties.meaning: Tursin, yashasin va oydek suluv qiz bo‘lsin

properties.name: Istakoy
properties.meaning: Qo‘msab, orzu qilib olingan oydek go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Istakxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Istak (Istak+xon)

properties.name: Istam
properties.meaning: Aynan: Tursin, qolsin, ya’ni umri uzoq bo‘lsin, o‘lmasin. Shakllari: Istamboy, Istamjon, Istamxon

properties.name: Istar
properties.meaning: Istara (qar.). Shakllari: Israroy

properties.name: Istara
properties.meaning: Istarasi issiq, yoqimtoy, jozibali. Sitora yulduzi nomidan. Shakllari: Istaraxon

properties.name: Istaram
properties.meaning: Qar. Mustaram

properties.name: Istat
properties.meaning: Tursin, qolsin, ya’ni o‘lmasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin. Asli: Istad, Istod

properties.name: Istatoy
properties.meaning: Qar. Istat (Istat+oy); oydek ko‘rkam qiz tursin, yashasin

properties.name: Istoda
properties.meaning: Turg‘un, sabotli, ya’ni yashaydigan bola

properties.name: Itoat, Itoatxon
properties.meaning: Itoatkor, mo‘min-qobil, odobli qiz

properties.name: Ifofat
properties.meaning: Poklik, pokizalik, tozalik

properties.name: Ifog‘at
properties.meaning: Sog‘ayish, tuzalish, sog‘ayib ketish

properties.name: Ifrat
properties.meaning: Ziyoda, ortiqcha, keragidan ortiq. Hadeb qiz tug‘ilavergan oilalarda o‘g‘il ko‘rishni orzu qilib berilgan ism

properties.name: Iffar
properties.meaning: Pokiza, ma’suma, bokira qiz

properties.name: Iffatbibi
properties.meaning: Or-nomusli, pokiza qiz

properties.name: Iffatbonu
properties.meaning: Pokiza, or-nomusli, aslzoda qiz

properties.name: Iffatjamol
properties.meaning: Pokiza va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Iffatoy
properties.meaning: Pokiza va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Ixlosa
properties.meaning: Sofdil, pokdomon, sadoqatli va xolis qiz

properties.name: Ixlosbonu
properties.meaning: Sofdil, pokdomon, aslzoda qiz

properties.name: Ixlosiya
properties.meaning: Soflik, samimiyat, sadoqat sohibasi

properties.name: Ixlosxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Ixlos (Ixlos+xon)

properties.name: Ishora
properties.meaning: Badanida qanqaydir belgi bilan tug‘ilgan qiz yoki Allohning xohishi, irodasi

properties.name: Ishorat
properties.meaning: Qar. Ishora. Shakli: Ishoratxon

properties.name: Ishqiya
properties.meaning: Muhabbat, mehru muruvvat sohibasi

properties.name: Iqboloy
properties.meaning: Baxtu saodatli, oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Iqlim
properties.meaning: Istarasi issiq, jozibali qiz yoki el, o‘lka farzandi. Shakllari: Iqlimoy, Iqlimxon, Iqlima

properties.name: Iqlima
properties.meaning: Qar. Iqlim (Iqlim+a)

properties.name: Iqlimbibi
properties.meaning: Qar. Iqlim (Iqlim+bibi)

properties.name: Iqlimbuvish
properties.meaning: Qar. Iqlim (Iqlim+buvish)

properties.name: Imrona
properties.meaning: Qarang

properties.name: Jabbor
properties.meaning: Mislsiz qudratli, bandalarining ishini isloh etuvchi, ularni gunohlari uchun jazolovchi. Jabbor nomi Allohning sifatlaridan biri. Asli: Abdujabbor (qar.)

properties.name: Jabborali
properties.meaning: Qar. Jabbor va Ali

properties.name: Jabborbergan
properties.meaning: Jabbor (qar.), ya’ni Alloh taolo bergan, ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Jabborberdi
properties.meaning: Jabbor (qar.), ya’ni Alloh taolo ato qildi, berdi

properties.name: Jabbormirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Jabbor va Mirza

properties.name: Jabborsodiq
properties.meaning: Qar. Jabbor va Sodiq

properties.name: Jabborsolih
properties.meaning: Jabbor (qar.) - Alloh taolo sa Solih (ezgu ishlar qiluvchi, Allohning irodasini bajo keltiruvchi) , ya’ni Muhammad (sav) ato etgan bola

properties.name: Jabborxon
properties.meaning: Jabbor (qar.), ya’ni Alloh ato qilgan martabali, ezozli o‘g‘il

properties.name: Jabborqul
properties.meaning: Jabborning, ya’ni Allohning bandasi, quli

properties.name: Jabin
properties.meaning: Aynan: peshona, manglay, ya’ni saodatli, baxtu-toleli bola yoki tuban, past bola. Ism keyingi manoda chaqaloq yomon ko‘zdan yiroq bo‘lsin, ko‘z tegmasin degan maqsadda beriladi

properties.name: Jabroil
properties.meaning: Allohdan payg‘ambarga vahiy keltiruvchi, vositachi farishta; Allohning askari, jangchisi. Ba’zan Allohning kuchi, qudrati deb ham talqin qilinadi

properties.name: Javdat
properties.meaning: Muruvvat, himmat, saxiylik; mehru-shafqat egasi

properties.name: Javdon, Javdonboy
properties.meaning: Javodon-mangu, doimiy, ya’ni umri uzoq va boqit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Javzo, Javzoboy
properties.meaning: Javzoda, ya’ni eroncha shamsiy yil hisobining 3 oyi (22 may-2 iyunga to‘g‘ri keladi)da tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Javli
properties.meaning: Oxirgi, kenja o‘g‘il javli  -  chavli - lochin, shunqor

properties.name: Javlon
properties.meaning: Chiroyli va shahdam qadamlar tashlovchi; harakatchan, chaqqon. Shakllar: Javlonbek, Javlonboy

properties.name: Javlonxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar nasliga mansub chaqqon va go‘zal bola

properties.name: Javlonqul
properties.meaning: Harakatchan va ko‘rkam bola yoki odobli, ahloqli

properties.name: Javman
properties.meaning: Jav so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi ismlarning qisqargan shakli

properties.name: Javod, Javodxon
properties.meaning: Muruvvatli, himmatli, saxovatli

properties.name: Javonbaxt
properties.meaning: Baxtli, baxtiyor, xushbaxt

properties.name: Javonboy
properties.meaning: Navqiron, ko‘rkam yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Javongar
properties.meaning: Boy, badavlat; kuchli, qudratli

properties.name: Javonsher
properties.meaning: Arslon bolasidek jasur, dovyurak bo‘lsin

properties.name: Javohir
properties.meaning: Qimmatbaho toshlar, zebu ziynatlar egasi, boy-badavlat bo‘lsin yoki bebaho, qimmatli

properties.name: Javshan,  Jovshon
properties.meaning: Qalqon (zirh, sovutdek) mustahkam bola yoki qar. Yozshan, Yozshanboy

properties.name: Javqa
properties.meaning: Eht.: Javqon, Javqora

properties.name: Javqiron
properties.meaning: Qar. Navqiron

properties.name: Javqon
properties.meaning: Jav - shuhratli; mashhur; ulug‘ hukmron

properties.name: Javqoch
properties.meaning: Go‘dakning yovi, ya’ni insu jinslar kochsin, bolaning umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Javqosh
properties.meaning: Qar. Javqoch

properties.name: Javhar
properties.meaning: Gavhardek qimmatli, bebaho bola yoki asl, nasab, farzand, yohud kuchli, qudratli, jasur

properties.name: Javharali
properties.meaning: Qar. Javhar va Ali

properties.name: Javhariddin
properties.meaning: Dinning qadrli, bebaho farzandi yoki dinning jasur, dovyurak posboni

properties.name: Jadalboy
properties.meaning: g‘ayratli, tezkor, mehnatkash

properties.name: Jadid
properties.meaning: Yosh, navqiron; yangi, toza, pokiza

properties.name: Jadra
properties.meaning: Yayrasin, quvnasin, ochilib-sochilin yursin

properties.name: Jazil
properties.meaning: Maqbul, durust, muqaddas yoki mahkam, irodali, mustahkam

properties.name: Jazilboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Jazil

properties.name: Jazo
properties.meaning: Oldingi turmagan bolalar evaziga (badaliga) berilgan sovg‘a  yoki iltijo qilib, tilab olingan bola

properties.name: Jaylov, Jaylovboy
properties.meaning: Yaylovda (o‘tloqda) tug‘ilgan bola yoki umri yaylov kabi bepayon, obod bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jaynoq
properties.meaning: Yayragan, yashnagan, quvnoq umr kechirsin

properties.name: Jaynoqmirza
properties.meaning: Hayoti quvnoq va bilimli, kelishgan yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jayron, Jayronboy
properties.meaning: Javron (ohu, kiyikdek) epchil va chaqqon yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jayxun
properties.meaning: Umri jayxun daryodek oqib tursin, jo‘shqin, farovon bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jakbar
properties.meaning: Qar. Akbar

properties.name: Jakbarali
properties.meaning: Qar. Akbarali

properties.name: Jala
properties.meaning: Kuchli jalla yog‘gan payti tug‘igan bola yoki umri jaladek serob bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jalid
properties.meaning: Puxta, chidamli, sobit, turg‘un

properties.name: Jalil
properties.meaning: Yuksak, ulug‘vor; dongdor, mashhur. Asli: Abdujalil (qar.)

properties.name: Jalis
properties.meaning: Otasiga hamsuhbat; yo‘ldosh, hamroh bo‘lib yursin

properties.name: Jalish
properties.meaning: Xushro‘y, go‘zal, ko‘rkam yoki Jaloliddin, Abdujalil ismlarining eq.shakli

properties.name: Jaloyir
properties.meaning: Jaloir qabilasiga mansub bola, jaloyir farzandi

properties.name: Jalol
properties.meaning: Buyuk, yuksak martabali; go‘zal, ko‘rkam

properties.name: Jaloliddin
properties.meaning: Dinning ulug‘vorligi, shavkati, shukuhi; dinnining buyukligi, mukammalligi yoki dinning ulug‘, shavkatli farzandi

properties.name: Jalolmirza
properties.meaning: Ulg‘ayib ulug‘vor, shavkatli hamda salobatli, o‘qimishli yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jalolxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodidan bo‘lgan, shavkatli, shukuhli bola

properties.name: Jalonboy
properties.meaning: Eht.: Javlonboy

properties.name: Jalg‘asin
properties.meaning: Ulansin, bog‘lansin, ya’ni oldingi bolalarga ko‘shilsin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Jalg‘ash, Jalg‘ashboy
properties.meaning: Ulansin, bog‘lansin, ya’ni oldingi bolalarga ko‘shilsin

properties.name: Jamal
properties.meaning: Tuya, erkak tuya, nortuya. Eht.: Jamol (qar.) ismining shakli

properties.name: Jaman, Jamanboy
properties.meaning: Yomon, yaramas bola. Chaqaloqqa jinu ajinalar e’tibor qilmasin, ko‘z tegmasin deb shunday ism beriladi. Shakllari: Jamantoy, Jamansho

properties.name: Jamanqora
