properties.meaning: Alloh bergan farzandlar bilan qanoatlandik, bolalar yetarli bo‘ldi yoki sabrli, toqatli bola. Asli: Qanoatulla (qar.). Shakllari: Qanoatjon, Qanoatxon, Qanoatsho

properties.name: Qanoatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning sabr-qanoatli bandasi

properties.name: Qanot
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib ota-onasiga suyanch, tayanch, qanot bo‘lsin yoki sog‘ ulgayib yuksak martabalarga erishsin, tolei baland bolsin. Shakllari: Qanotboy, Qanotxon

properties.name: Qantar, Qantarboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Qangtarboy

properties.name: Qaramon
properties.meaning: Qorachadan kelgan, qora bola yoki muhofazaga olingan yohud qaramon urug‘iga mansub bola

properties.name: Qarbug‘a
properties.meaning: Jasur, yengilmas, qahramon

properties.name: Qari, Qarri
properties.meaning: Marhum bobosining ismi bilan atalgan bola

properties.name: Qarishqul
properties.meaning: Bo‘ri, qashqir. Sol: Bo‘ri, Bo‘riboy

properties.name: Qarshi
properties.meaning: Avvalgi turmagan bolalarning aksi, sog‘ ulg‘ayuvchi bola yoki tug‘ilishi qiyin kechgan bola. Shakllari: Qarshiboy, Qarshigul, Qarshijon, Qarshioy

properties.name: Qarshimat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qarshimuhammad

properties.name: Qarshimurod
properties.meaning: Qar. Qarshi va Murod

properties.name: Qarshitoy
properties.meaning: Erka, suyukli bola eson-omon ulg‘aysin

properties.name: Qarqara
properties.meaning: Turnaga o‘xshash va bo‘ynidan yuqorisi qora rangli qush yoki qarqara urug‘iga mansub bola

properties.name: Qashqartoy
properties.meaning: Eht.: Qo‘chqortoy yoki Qashqar (shahar) nomidan olingan ism

properties.name: Qashqir, Qashqirboy
properties.meaning: Bo‘ri. Sol: Bo‘ri, Bo‘riboy

properties.name: Qayum
properties.meaning: Qar. Qayyum

properties.name: Qahramon
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, bahodir, dovyurak. Eht.: Qahramon-qayrog‘ich, ya’ni qayrog‘ichdek mustahkam, chidamli bo‘lsin yohud qaramon urug‘i farzandi

properties.name: Qahraton
properties.meaning: Qattiq sovuqli qishda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qahhor
properties.meaning: Qahr qiluvchi, barchani bo‘ysindiruvchi, g‘olib. Bu nom Allohning sifatlaridan biridir. Asli: Abduqahhor (qar.)

properties.name: Qahhorali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qahhor va Ali

properties.name: Qahhorgul
properties.meaning: Qahhorning (qar.), ya’ni Allohning quli, bandasi

properties.name: Qivomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning adolatli, haqgo‘y ixlosmandi

properties.name: Qiyom
properties.meaning: Qar. Qiyomiddin. Shakllari: Qiyomboy, Qiyomjon

properties.name: Qiyomiddin
properties.meaning: Ibodat payti, quyosh tik kelganda tug‘ilgan bola yoki tiklovchi, dinni oyoqqa turg‘azuvchi, dinni yuksaltiruvchi bola

properties.name: Qiyosboy
properties.meaning: o‘rnak, namuna bo‘luvchi bola

properties.name: Qiyot, Qiyotboy
properties.meaning: Qiyot kabilasiga mansub bola, qiyot farzandi

properties.name: Qiyofat
properties.meaning: Ko‘rinish, siymo; yuz, chehra

properties.name: Qiybosar
properties.meaning: Qiylarni bosib yurib ketsin, sog‘ ulg‘aysin

properties.name: Qilich
properties.meaning: Qilichdek keskir va mustahkam yoki kindigi qilich bilan kesilgan bola yohud g‘olib, muzaffar bola. Shakllari: Qilichboy, Qilichxon, Qilichbek, Qilichjon

properties.name: Qilichberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh qilichdek keskir, mustahkam o‘g‘il berdi

properties.name: Qilichmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qilichmuhammad

properties.name: Qilichmirza
properties.meaning: Qilichdek o‘tkir, mustahkam va mirzalardek o‘qimishli, kelishgan yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qilichmuhammad
properties.meaning: Qilichdek o‘tkir, mustahkam yigit bo‘lsin va Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qilichniyoz
properties.meaning: Allohdan iltijolar qilib so‘rab olingan qilichdek o‘tkir bola

properties.name: Qilichturdi
properties.meaning: Qilichdek mustahkam bo‘lib tursin, ya’ni yashasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qilichtursin
properties.meaning: Qilichdek mustahkam bola tursin, yashasin

properties.name: Qilichxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qilich (Qilich+xon)

properties.name: Qimmat
properties.meaning: Qadr-qimmatli, e’zozli qiz. Shakllari: Qimmatboy, Qimmatqul, Qimmatoy

properties.name: Qimmatali
properties.meaning: Qimmatli, aziz o‘g‘ilni Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qimmatqul
properties.meaning: Allohning qadrli, e’zozga sazovor bandasi, quli

properties.name: Qipchoq
properties.meaning: Qipchoq qabilasiga mansub bola, qipchoq (qadimiy turkiy qabila) farzandi

properties.name: Qipchoqqul
properties.meaning: Allohning qipchoq urug‘iga mansub bandasi (quli) yoki qipchoq urug‘ining sodiq farzandi

properties.name: Qirjigit
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib, balog‘atga yetgan, qirchin yigit bo‘lsin yoki qir, dala farzandi

properties.name: Qirov
properties.meaning: Birinchi qirov (shabnam) tushgan paytda tug‘ilgan bola yoki qirov - o‘tkir, keskir bola

properties.name: Qironboy
properties.meaning: Zo‘r, zabardast, saodatli yoki ikki sayyora bir burjda to‘qnashgan paytda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qirg‘iz, Qirg‘izboy
properties.meaning: Bolaning ko‘rinishi qirg‘izga o‘xshagani uchun berilgan ism yoki qirg‘izlar orasida tugilgan bola

properties.name: Qirg‘izali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qirg‘iz va Ali

properties.name: Qirg‘iy
properties.meaning: Qirg‘iydek epchil, chaqqon, jasur bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qobil
properties.meaning: Iste’dodli, qobiliyatli; kuchli, qudratli yoki yovvosh, tarbiya ko‘rgan yohud orzu va tilaklarimiz bajo bo‘lib berilgan bola. Shakllari: Qobilboy, Qobiljon, Qobilbu, Qobilxon

properties.name: Qobilgora
properties.meaning: Qar. Qobil va Qora

properties.name: Qobul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qobil

properties.name: Qovunboy
properties.meaning: Qovun pishig‘ida yoki qovun, ya’ni poliz tepasiga ko‘chib chiqqanda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qovus
properties.meaning: Qavs oyi (shamsiya yil hisobining 9 oyi 22 noyabr - 21 dekabrga to‘g‘ri keladi) da tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qodir
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, barcha narsaga layoqatli. Bu nom Allohning sifatlaridan biridir. Asli: Abduqodir (qar.). Shakllari: Qodirbek, Qodirjon, Qodirxon

properties.name: Qodirali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodir va Ali

properties.name: Qodirbek
properties.meaning: Beklar avlodiga mansub kuchli, qudratli bola

properties.name: Qodirbergan
properties.meaning: Qodir (qar.), ya’ni Alloh ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Qodirberdi
properties.meaning: Qodir (qar.), ya’ni Alloh bergan tuhfa

properties.name: Qodiriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning kuchi, qudrati yoki dinning sodiq muhlisi

properties.name: Qodirmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodirmuhammad

properties.name: Qodirmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodirmuhammad

properties.name: Qodirmurod
properties.meaning: Alloh yetkazgan orzu, maqsad

properties.name: Qodirnazar
properties.meaning: Qodir, ya’ni Allohnig iltifoti, etibori (nazari) tufayli erishilgan bola

properties.name: Qodirniyoz
properties.meaning: Qodir, ya’ni Allohnig tuhfasi, sovg‘asi yoki Allohdan tilanib olingan bola

properties.name: Qodirxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodir (Qodir+xon) yoki hokim, boshliq, sarkor

properties.name: Qodirxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodir va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Qodirqul
properties.meaning: Allohning bandasi (quli). Sol: Abduqodir

properties.name: Qodirg‘iyoz
properties.meaning: Qar. Qodirniyoz. Eht.: Qodir va g‘iyos

properties.name: Qozi
properties.meaning: Ulg‘ayib adolatpesha, diniy hakam bo‘lsin yoki qozi bo‘lib o‘tgan bobosining ismi berilgan bola. Shakllari: Qoziboy, Qozixon, Qozibek

properties.name: Qozimurod
properties.meaning: Qar. Qozi va Murod

properties.name: Qoziqul
properties.meaning: o‘zini diniy adolat yo‘liga bag‘ishlagan bola

properties.name: Qozoq
properties.meaning: Ko‘rinishi qozoqqa o‘xshagani uchun shunday atalgan yoki erkin, hur, ozod yohud uyga qozoq mehmon kelganda yoki qozoqlar orasida tug‘ilgan bola ham shunday nomlanadi. Shakllari: Qozoqboy, Qozoqxon

properties.name: Qoim, Qoyim
properties.meaning: Turg‘un, sobit, mustahkam; ustuvor, poydor; yashaydigan yoki nishona yohud o‘rinbosar, noib. Eht.: Qayyum (qar.)

properties.name: Qoldi
properties.meaning: o‘g‘ir kasallikdan so‘ng sog‘ qolgan bola yoki Qolli - Xolli - xol bilan tugilgan bola. Shakllari: Qoldiboy, Qoldigul, Qoldiqul

properties.name: Qoldiqul
properties.meaning: Alloh sog‘ qolgan quli yoki Allohning xolli bandasi, quli

properties.name: Qoldoim
properties.meaning: Doimo sog‘ tursin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qoljon
properties.meaning: Qar. Xoljon

properties.name: Qolqon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qalqon

properties.name: Qondim
properties.meaning: Farzandlarim yetarli bo‘ldi, qanoat hosil qildim, boshqa tug‘mayman ma’nosida yoki cho‘l o‘simligi - qondim kabi chidamli, mustahkam bolsin

properties.name: Qondiq
properties.meaning: Farzandga qanoat hosil qildik, boshqa tug‘masam ham mayli

properties.name: Qoniq
properties.meaning: Farzandlarga qoniqdik, bolalarimiz yetarli

properties.name: Qonqora
properties.meaning: Qar. Honqora

properties.name: Qoplon
properties.meaning: Qoplondek dovyurak, jasur bo‘lib o‘ssin yoki asad oyi (iyul) da tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qoplonbek
properties.meaning: Beklar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan dovyurak, jasur bola

properties.name: Qoplonmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Qoplon va Mirza

properties.name: Qora
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli bola yoki qoracha bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola yohud qoracha urug‘iga (qirq qabilasi tarmog‘i) mansub bola. Shakllari: Qorabek, Qoraboy, Qorajon, Qoratoy, Qoraxon, Qoraqul

properties.name: Qoraboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora (Qora+boy)

properties.name: Qorabarlos
properties.meaning: Qora barlos urug‘iga mansub bola

properties.name: Qoraberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh kuchli, qudratli o‘g‘il ato qildi yoki Allohning tuhfasi

properties.name: Qorabola
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli bola yoki qora tusli (qorachadan kelgan) bola, keyingi holda laqab ismga aylanib ketgan

properties.name: Qorabotir
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, bahodir; jasur bola

properties.name: Qorabosh
properties.meaning: Qul, cho‘ri yoki burgut yohud timqora sochli bola

properties.name: Qorako‘z
properties.meaning: Ko‘zlari qora bola; go‘zal, ko‘rkam bola

properties.name: Qoramirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Mirza

properties.name: Qoramamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qoramuhammad

properties.name: Qoramuhammad
properties.meaning: Kuchli, dovyurak o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qoramulla
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Mulla

properties.name: Qoramurod
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli yigit bo‘lsin va ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Qoraniyoz
properties.meaning: Allohdan iltijolar bilan tilab olingan bola ulg‘ayib kuchli, qudratli yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qorapo‘lat
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli va po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Qorasunqur
properties.meaning: Burgut, shunqordek kuchli, jasur yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qorategin
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli shohzoda, hukmron

properties.name: Qoratoy
properties.meaning: Qulun (1 yoshli toy) dek bola, ya’ni qulundek o‘ynoqlab, yayrab o‘ssin yoki Qora+toy kuchli, qudratli va suyukli, erkatoy bola

properties.name: Qoratosh
properties.meaning: Zabardast qora toshdek mahkam, mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qoraxon
properties.meaning: Ulug‘, qudratli xon

properties.name: Qoraxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar nasliga mansub qudratli, jasur bola

properties.name: Qoracha
properties.meaning: Qoramag‘iz bola yoki qoracha urug‘iga (laqay qabilasi tarkibida) mansub bola

properties.name: Qorachori
properties.meaning: To‘rtinchi o‘g‘il (farzand) kuchli, dovyurak yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qorao‘glon
properties.meaning: Qudratli, bahodir o‘g‘il

properties.name: Qoraqul
properties.meaning: Allohning kuchli, qudratli bandasi yoki soqchi, posbon, qoravul

properties.name: Qoraqursoq
properties.meaning: Ushbu nomdagi urug‘ farzandi

properties.name: Qoraqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Qo‘zi

properties.name: Qorag‘ach
properties.meaning: Qorag‘ochdek chidamli, mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qoraahmad
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Ahmad. Sol: Ahmadqora

properties.name: Qorahasan
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Hasan. Sol: Hasanqora

properties.name: Qorahusan
properties.meaning: Qar. Qora va Husan. Sol: Husnqora

properties.name: Qorbo‘ta
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ganda tug‘ilgan bo‘taloqdek, chiroyli, suyukli bola

properties.name: Qoryog‘
properties.meaning: Qar. Qoryog‘di

properties.name: Qoryog‘di
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ganda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qorjigit
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ayotganda tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il ulgayib katta yigit bolsin yoki birinchi qorni boshlab kelgan bola

properties.name: Qorjob
properties.meaning: Qar. Qorjovul

properties.name: Qorjovul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qoryog‘di

properties.name: Qorjon
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ayotganda tug‘ilgan suyukli bola

properties.name: Qori
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib Qur’onni yoddan qiroat qiluvchi (qori) bo‘lsin yoki marhum qori bobosining ismi bilan nomlangan bola

properties.name: Qoriburhon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori va Burhon

properties.name: Qoriyoqub
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori va Yoqub

properties.name: Qorijon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori (Qori+jon) yoki Qorajon

properties.name: Qorizokir
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori va Zokir

properties.name: Qoriyo‘ldosh
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori va Yo‘ldosh

properties.name: Qoriniyoz
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori va Niyoz

properties.name: Qorixon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qori (Qori+xon)

properties.name: Qoriqul
properties.meaning: Allohning xudojo‘y, toat-ibodat qiluvchi bandasi (quli)

properties.name: Qorkeldi
properties.meaning: Birinchi qorni olib kelgan, birinchi qor yog‘ayotganda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qorli, Qorliboy
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ganda tug‘ilgan, qorni olib kelgan bola

properties.name: Qormurod
properties.meaning: Birinchi qor yog‘ganda tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il ulgayib murodu maqsadiga yetsin yoki birinchi qor yogganda erishilgan orzuimiz

properties.name: Qorun
properties.meaning: Boyli, davlat; Xorun (Qorundek) boy-badavlat bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qosid
properties.meaning: Qar. Qosidulla

properties.name: Qosidulla
properties.meaning: Allohning xabarlarini yetkazuvchi, Allohning elchisi

properties.name: Qosim
properties.meaning: Taqsimlovchi, inson qismatini belgilovchi. Bu nom Muhammad (sav) o‘g‘lining ismi bo‘lgan. Shakllari: Qosimboy, Qosimjon, Qosimbek, Qosimtoy

properties.name: Qosimali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qosim va Ali

properties.name: Qosimberdi
properties.meaning: Rizq-ro‘zni tarqatuvchi, inson qismatini belgilovchi, ya’ni Alloh bergan bola

properties.name: Qosimyor
properties.meaning: Rizq-ro‘z, nasiba taqsimlovchi, ya’ni Alloh qo‘llab yursin

properties.name: Qosimtoy
properties.meaning: Qosim, ya’ni Alloh bergan suyukli, erka bola

properties.name: Qosimxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Qosim va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Qosimsho
properties.meaning: Qar. Qosim va Sho(h)

properties.name: Qosimqul
properties.meaning: Qosim, ya’ni Allohning bandasi, quli

properties.name: Qohir
properties.meaning: Zabardast, qudratli; faxr qilsa arziydigan; g‘olib, muzaffar

properties.name: Quvabek
properties.meaning: Quva urug‘iga mansub bola yoki quvva - kuchli, qudratli bola

properties.name: Quvamurod
properties.meaning: Quva shahrida erishilgan orzu, armon, ya’ni Quvada tug‘ilgan bola yoki quva urug‘ining murod-maqsadli farzandi

properties.name: Quvvat
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli; chidamli, mahkam. Shakllari: Quvvatbek, Quvvatboy

properties.name: Quvvatali
properties.meaning: Alining iltifoti, ko‘magi bilan topilgan bola yoki Alidek kuchli, qudratli bo‘lsin

properties.name: Quvvatxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub kuchli, qudratli bola

properties.name: Quvnoq
properties.meaning: Quvnoq, shodon, baxtiyor bo‘lib o‘ssin

properties.name: Quvomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning haqiqatparvar, adolatpesha kishisi

properties.name: Quvon
properties.meaning: Qar. Quvondik. Shakllari: Quvonboy, Quvonjon, Quvontoy

properties.name: Quvondiq
properties.meaning: o‘g‘illik bo‘lganimiz uchun shodlikka to‘ldik yoki quvonch, baxtiyorlik boisi bolgan ogil yohud quvondiq urugiga (argin, laqay qabilalari tarkibida) mansub bola

properties.name: Quvonsin
properties.meaning: Shodlanib, baxtiyor bo‘lib o‘ssin

properties.name: Quvontoy
properties.meaning: Erka, suyukli o‘g‘il quvnab, yayrab o‘ssin

properties.name: Quvontur
properties.meaning: Sog‘ omon tursin va shodon bo‘lib o‘ssin

properties.name: Quvonch
properties.meaning: Ota-onasiga quvonch, shodlik keltirgan bola. Shakli: Quvonchxon

properties.name: Quddus
properties.meaning: Pok, pokiza, begunoh, muqaddas; aziz; ilohiy. Falastindagi Dovud payg‘ambar barpo qilgan shahar nomi. Shuningdek bu nom Allohi Taoloning sifatlaridan biri bo‘lib, nuqsonlardan xoli ma’nosini anglatadi. Qar. Abduquddus

properties.name: Qudrat
properties.meaning: Quvvatli, kuchli, qodir. Asli: Qudratulla

properties.name: Qudratali
properties.meaning: Alining qudrati, iltifoti tufayli tug‘ilgan bola; Alining tuhfasi

properties.name: Qudratulla
properties.meaning: Allohning qudrati, irodasi bilan tug‘ilgan bola yoki badanida qandaydir g‘ayritabiiy belgi, nuqson bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Quyonboy
properties.meaning: Sezgir, ziyrak yoki quyon yilida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Quyosh
properties.meaning: Tolei quyoshdek porloq bo‘lsinl quyosh farzandi yoki go‘zal, zebo. Shakllari: Quyoshbek, Quyoshboy, Quyoshjon

properties.name: Qul
properties.meaning: Qul so‘zi bilan boshlangan va oxirida qul so‘zi qo‘shilgan qo‘shma ismlarning (Qulmuhammad, Muhammadqul) eq.shakli. Qul - xizmatchi, tobe, banda; erksiz

properties.name: Qulay
properties.meaning: Qul so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlarning (Qulahmad, Qulmurod) shakli yoki muloyim, yoqimli, odobli

properties.name: Qulali
properties.meaning: Alining xizmatkori, Aliga sodiq. Sol: Aliqul

properties.name: Qulahmad
properties.meaning: Ahmadning (Muhammad payg‘ambar) xizmatkori, Ahmadga sodiq kishi. Sol: Ahmadqul

properties.name: Qulbashar
properties.meaning: Xalq, insoniyat xizmatkori

properties.name: Qulbek
properties.meaning: Qullarning boshlig‘i, sardori yoki Allohning beklar avlodidan bo‘lgan xizmatkori (quli)

properties.name: Qulberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan xizmatkori, yordamchi yoki berganning, yaratganning quli. Sol: Berdiqul

properties.name: Qulbobo
properties.meaning: Marhum bobosining ismi berilgan bola. Sol: Boboqul

properties.name: Qulbozor
properties.meaning: Allohning bozor kuni tug‘ilgan bandasi.Sol: Bozorqul

properties.name: Qulboy
properties.meaning: Allohning boy-badavlat bandasi. Sol: Boyqul

properties.name: Qulbotir
properties.meaning: Allohning jasur, dovyurak bandasi. Sol: Botirqul

properties.name: Qulbosh
properties.meaning: Qullarning boshlig‘i, sardori

properties.name: Qulboq
properties.meaning: Eht.: Qulbaxt, Qulboqi

properties.name: Qulbo‘ta
properties.meaning: Allohning erkatoy, suyukli bandasi. Sol: Bo‘taqul

properties.name: Quldavlat
properties.meaning: Allohning boy-badavlat bandasi. Sol: Davlatqul

properties.name: Quldor
properties.meaning: Qullar egasi, boy-badavlat hukmdor yoki o‘g‘illari ko‘p bo‘lgan kishi

properties.name: Quljon
properties.meaning: Suyukli, erka qul, ya’ni o‘g‘il

properties.name: Quljuma
properties.meaning: Allohning juma kuni tug‘ilgan bandasi, sodiq xizmatchisi. Sol: Jumaqul

properties.name: Quli
properties.meaning: Oxirida qul, quli so‘zlari bilan kelgan qo‘shma ismlarning (Ollohqul, Olloquli kabi) eq.shakli. Shakllari: Quliboy, Qulijon, Qulibek

properties.name: Qulin, Qulinboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Qulunboy

properties.name: Qulkeldi
properties.meaning: Allohning sodiq, bandasi dunyoga keldi, tug‘ildi. Qar. Keldiqul

properties.name: Qulli, Qulliboy
properties.meaning: Qul so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlar (Qulmurod, Qulmuhammad)ning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qulluq
properties.meaning: o‘g‘il bergani uchun Allohga qulluq qilamiz

properties.name: Qulmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qulmuhammad

properties.name: Qulman, Qulmon
properties.meaning: Qul so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlar (Qulmuhammad, Qulniyoz, Qulnazar)ning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qulmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qulmuhammad

properties.name: Qulmiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning sodiq xizmatkori, haqqoniy dinchi, xudojo‘y

properties.name: Qulmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Mirzaqul

properties.name: Qulmurod
properties.meaning: Allohning sodiq bandasi ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Qulmuhammad
properties.meaning: Muhammad (sav)ning sodiq xizmatkori (quli) bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qulmo‘min
properties.meaning: Allohning yovvosh, mo‘min-qobil bandasi (quli). Sol: Mo‘minqul

properties.name: Qulnazar
properties.meaning: Allohning e’tibori (nazari) tushgan bola, Allohning iltifoti, muruvvati tufayli tug‘ilgan bola. Sol: Nazarqul

properties.name: Qulniyoz
properties.meaning: Allohdan yolvorib, so‘rab olingan bola yoki Allohning tuhfasi, sovg‘asi. Sol: Niyozqul

properties.name: Qulomon
properties.meaning: Allohning sodiq bandasi bo‘lgan bola sog‘-omon ulg‘aysin

properties.name: Qulontoy, Qulonjon
properties.meaning: Qulondek ziyrak, sog‘lom bo‘lsin yoki qulon (qulonchi) urug‘iga mansub bola

properties.name: Qulota
properties.meaning: Qar. Otaqul

properties.name: Qulsaid
properties.meaning: Qar. Saidqul

properties.name: Qulsari
properties.meaning: Qar. Sariqul

properties.name: Qulsoat
properties.meaning: Qar. Soatqul

properties.name: Qultoy
properties.meaning: Allohning erka, suyukli bandasi yoki erka qul. Eht.: Qultoy<Qultosh<Gul+toy (qar.)

properties.name: Qultosh
properties.meaning: Allohning toshdek mustahkam bandasi (quli); eht.: yoki Qultosh<Kultosh<Gultosh

properties.name: Qulturdi
properties.meaning: Qar. Turdiqul

properties.name: Qulto‘ra
properties.meaning: Qar. To‘raqul

properties.name: Qulunboy
properties.meaning: Qulun (1 yillik toy, emuvchi toychoq)dek go‘zal bola yoki qulundek o‘ynoqlab, yayrab o‘ssin

properties.name: Quluntoy
properties.meaning: Toychoqdek yayrab, shodlanib o‘ssin

properties.name: Qulfiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning mustahkamligi, dinning irodali, sobitqadam farzandi yoki dinning gullab-yashnashi, dinning rivoji, go‘zalligi

properties.name: Qulcha
properties.meaning: Jajji, kichik, kenja qul

properties.name: Qulqora
properties.meaning: Qar. Qoraqul

properties.name: Qulqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘ziqul

properties.name: Qumriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning beozor, yovvosh bolasi

properties.name: Qunduzali
properties.meaning: Qunduzdek, chiroyli, go‘zal yigitni Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qunduzboy
properties.meaning: Qunduzdek chiroyli yigit

properties.name: Qunon
properties.meaning: Qunondek (uch yashar erkak ot) sho‘xchan va qudratli yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Quranboy
properties.meaning: Qurbonnazar, Qurbonniyoz ismlarning eq.shakli yoki qar. Qurbon, Qurbonoy

properties.name: Quraq
properties.meaning: Qar. Quroqboy

properties.name: Qurbat
properties.meaning: Yaqinlashishi, yetishish, orzuga erishish; qarindoshlik, samimiyat; Allohga yaqinlashish

properties.name: Qurbek
properties.meaning: Jasur, mard, bahodir yoki qobiliyatli, qurbli, munosib, qimmatli

properties.name: Qurbon
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida (qamariya yil hisobining 12-zulxijja oyi), qurbon hayiti kunlarida tug‘ilgan bola. Shakllari: Qurbonboy, Qurbonbek, Qurbonbeka, Qurbonbu, Qurbonoy, Qurbonbibi

properties.name: Qurbonali
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘ilni Ali o‘z panohida asrasin yoki Aliga hadya qilingan, qurbon qilingan bola

properties.name: Qurbonbek
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan beklar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Qurbonberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh qurbon oyida ato qilgan bola; Allohning qurbon oyida bergan tuhfasi

properties.name: Qurbonboqi
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘ilning umri uzoq, boqiy bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qurbonvali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbon va Vali

properties.name: Qurbonyoz
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbonniyoz

properties.name: Qurbonkeldi
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qurbonmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbonmuhammad

properties.name: Qurbonmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbonmuhammad

properties.name: Qurbonmurod
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida erishilgan orzu, armon yoki qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib murodu maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Qurbonmuhammad
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin yoki Muhammadga bagishlangan, baxshida qilingan bola

properties.name: Qurbonnabi
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbon va Nabi

properties.name: Qurbonnazar
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan va Allohning nazari tushgan bola

properties.name: Qurbonniyoz
properties.meaning: Alloh qurbon oyida yuborgan sovg‘a, ehson yoki Allohdan o‘tinib tilab olingan va qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qurbonpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Qurbonsaid
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan, tolei baland, baxtli bola

properties.name: Qurbonsihat
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il sihat-salomat bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qurbonsoat
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyining baxtli, qutli soatida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qurbonsuyun
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida erishilgan shodlik, baxtiyorlik

properties.name: Qurbontoy
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan suyukli, erka bola

properties.name: Qurbonturdi
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan bola turib qoladi, yashaydi deb umid qilamiz

properties.name: Qurbontursun
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan bola turib qolsin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qurbonxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan xo‘jalar, oqsuyaklar nasliga mansub bola

properties.name: Qurbonsho
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbon va Sho(h)

properties.name: Qurbonqilich
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il qilichdek o‘tkir va mustahkam bolsin

properties.name: Qurbong‘ozi
properties.meaning: Dinning qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan g‘olib kurashchisi, himoyachisi

properties.name: Qurbug‘a
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, jasur; yengilmas, bahodir

properties.name: Qurdosh
properties.meaning: Boshqa bolalarga tengqur, tengdosh bo‘lib o‘ssin

properties.name: Qurishjon
properties.meaning: Qurush - mahkam, mustahkam yoki qurch  -  quruch - istak, tilak, orzu, ya’ni istalgan, orzu qilingan bola. Yana sol: Qurch  -  Quruch

properties.name: Qurniyoz
properties.meaning: Qar. Qurbonniyoz

properties.name: Qurol
properties.meaning: Quralgi, yamalgin, ulangin, ya’ni sog‘ bo‘lib boshqa bolalar, ota-onaga qo‘shilsin. Shakllari: Qurolbek, Qurolboy, Quroloy. Sol: Qo‘roqboy

properties.name: Quron, Quronboy
properties.meaning: Ko‘paysin, unsin (o‘ssin) yoki quran (oltoy - mo‘gulcha) - guran  -  xuran - uch, uchinchi, ya’ni oiladagi uchinchi bola

properties.name: Quroboy
properties.meaning: Yamaluvchi, bog‘lanuvchi, birlashuvchi bola, ya’ni ota-onasiga, boshqa bolalarga ulanib ketsin, yashasin, o‘lmasin

properties.name: Qutbiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning qutbi, markazi; dinning asosi, tayanchi

properties.name: Qutboy
properties.meaning: Baxtli, saodatmand yoki rizqu nasibasi butun bola

properties.name: Qutbulla
properties.meaning: Allohning nazariga sazovor; aziz, e’zozli bola

properties.name: Qutvali
properties.meaning: Allohning baxtli va saodatmand xizmatkori; xudojo‘y

properties.name: Qutjon
properties.meaning: Baxtli, quli va aziz, suyukli bola

properties.name: Qutim
properties.meaning: Qut so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlarning (Qutlimurod) eq.shakli

properties.name: Qutli
properties.meaning: Baxtli, saodatli, xosiyatli bola. Shakllari: Qutlibek, Qutliboy

properties.name: Qutliali
properties.meaning: Baxtli, saodatmand o‘g‘ilni Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qutliberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh baxtli, tolei baland o‘g‘il berdi

properties.name: Qutliboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutli (Qutli+boy)

properties.name: Qutlibo‘lar
properties.meaning: Baxtli, saodatmand odam bo‘ladi, deb umid qilamiz

properties.name: Qutliyor
properties.meaning: Baxt-saodat, istiqbol yor bo‘ladigan bola yoki baxtli do‘st

properties.name: Qutlijon
properties.meaning: Baxtli-saodatli hamda suyukli bola

properties.name: Qutlizamon
properties.meaning: Zamonasining baxtli bolasi

properties.name: Qutliyol
properties.meaning: Tolei baland, kelajagi porloq bola

properties.name: Qutlikeldi
properties.meaning: Baxtli, xosiyatli bola tug‘ildi, dunyoga keldi

properties.name: Qutlimamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutlimuhammad

properties.name: Qutlimardon
properties.meaning: Erkaklarning, mardlarning eng baxtli, saodatlisi

properties.name: Qutlimat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutlimuhammad

properties.name: Qutlimirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutli va Mirza

properties.name: Qutlimurod
properties.meaning: Baxtli, saodatli o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Qutlimuhammad
properties.meaning: Baxtli o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin yoki Muhammad (sav) baxsh etgan baxt, saodat

properties.name: Qutlinazar
properties.meaning: Allohning nazari, mehri tushgan baxtli bola yoki Allohning mehri, muruvvati (nazari) bilan tug‘ilgan baxtli bola

properties.name: Qutliniyoz
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan qutlug‘, baxtli bola yoki Allohdan tilanib, so‘rab olingan baxtli bola

properties.name: Qutliposhsha
properties.meaning: Baxtli va ulug‘ martabali bola yoki baxtli, saodatmand hukmron, shoh

properties.name: Qutlipo‘lat
properties.meaning: Baxtli va po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Qutlirahmon
properties.meaning: Alloh (Rahmon)ning saodatli bandasi; Qar. Qutli va Rahmon

properties.name: Qutlitemir
properties.meaning: Baxtli va temirdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Qutlixon
properties.meaning: Saodatmand, tolei baland hukmron, shoh

properties.name: Qutlixo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodidan bo‘lgan baxtli, omadli bola

properties.name: Qutlisho
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutli va Sho(h)

properties.name: Qutliq
properties.meaning: Baxtli, omadli bola yoki shodligimiz boisi bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Qutliqjon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutliq (Qutliq+jon)

properties.name: Qutliqadam
properties.meaning: Qadami xosiyatli, qutlug‘; baxt omad sohibi bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Qutliqul
properties.meaning: Allohning baxtli, saodatmand bandasi

properties.name: Qutliesh
properties.meaning: Baxtli, omadli do‘st yoki baxtli bo‘lsin va otasiga (o‘zidan oldingi) bolalarga hamdam, esh bo‘lib ossin

properties.name: Qutlug‘
properties.meaning: Baxtli, omadli va qadami qutlug‘ bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qutlug‘murod
properties.meaning: Murodu maqsadimiz, orzuimiz bo‘lgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib, baxtli, saodatli bolsin

properties.name: Qutmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutlimuhammad

properties.name: Qutmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutlimuhammad

properties.name: Qutmon, Qutman
properties.meaning: Qut so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlar (Qutmuhammad, Qutlimurod)ning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qutfiddin
properties.meaning: Qar. Qutbiddin

properties.name: Qutchi
properties.meaning: Baxt, saodat sohibi, baxtiyor bola

properties.name: Qushbegi
properties.meaning: Bu nom o‘tmishda Buxoro va Xiva xonligida xonning ovchilik (shikor) bilan bog‘liq ishlarini tashkil qiluvchi amaldorlarning unvoni bo‘lgan

properties.name: Qushbek
properties.meaning: Qar. Qushbek

properties.name: Qushboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushboy

properties.name: Quyunboy
properties.meaning: Qattiq quyun paytida tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qo‘zi
properties.meaning: Suyukli, erkatoy bola yoki molli-davlatli bo‘lsin yohud qo‘ylar qo‘zilagan mavsumda tug‘ilgan bola. Shakllari: Qoziboy, Qozibek, Qozixon

properties.name: Qo‘zibola
properties.meaning: Erkatoy, suyukli bola

properties.name: Qo‘ziboqar
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib qo‘zilarni boquvchi; boy-badavlat bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qo‘zivon
properties.meaning: Qo‘zilarni boquvchi; qo‘ychibon yoki sog‘ ulg‘ayib qoylari kop, badavlat bolsin

properties.name: Qo‘ziyor
properties.meaning: Suyukli, erka o‘g‘ilga Alloh o‘ziyor bo‘lsin yoki boylik, davlat sohibi

properties.name: Qo‘zim
properties.meaning: Erkatoyim, suyuklim yoki qo‘zi so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qo‘zimurod
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘zi va Murod

properties.name: Qo‘ziturdi
properties.meaning: Erka, suyukli o‘g‘il tursin, yashasin

properties.name: Qo‘zixon
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘zi (Qo‘zi+xon)

properties.name: Qo‘ziqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘zi (Qo‘zi+qul)

properties.name: Qo‘zihaydar
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘zi va Haydar

properties.name: Qo‘yboq
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘yboqar

properties.name: Qo‘yboqar
properties.meaning: Ulg‘ayib qo‘zilarni boqsin, ya’ni qo‘ylari, mol-dunyosi ko‘p, badavlat bolsin

properties.name: Qo‘ydiqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘yliqul

properties.name: Qo‘yli, Qo‘yliboy
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib qo‘ylari ko‘p, badavlat bolsin

properties.name: Qo‘yliqul
properties.meaning: Allohning boy-badavlat bandasi (quli)

properties.name: Qo‘ymurod
properties.meaning: Murodu maqsadimiz, orzuimiz bo‘lgan bola ulg‘ayib murodiga yetsin

properties.name: Qo‘ysin
properties.meaning: Tinch, osoyishta bo‘lsin, yashasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Qo‘ysinboy, Qo‘ysinoy, Qoysinxon

properties.name: Qo‘ychi
properties.meaning: Oldida qo‘ylari, mollari ko‘p, boy-badavlat bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Qo‘ychibek, Qoychiboy

properties.name: Qo‘ychiqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘ychi (Qo‘ychi+qul)

properties.name: Qo‘ldosh
properties.meaning: Do‘st, o‘rtoq; yordamchi, ko‘makdosh

properties.name: Qo‘ldoshali
properties.meaning: Alining hamdami, yo‘ldoshi yoki Ali qo‘llaydigan bola

properties.name: Qo‘ldoshmat
properties.meaning: Muhammad (sav) qo‘llaydigan bola yoki Muhammadning hamdami, unga sig‘inuvchi bola

properties.name: Qo‘non
properties.meaning: Tinch, xotirjam, rohatda yashovchi yoki qar. Qunon

properties.name: Qo‘noqboy
properties.meaning: Mehmonga borganda tug‘ilgan bola yoki qo‘noq (tariqning turi) pishganda tug‘ilgan bola. Shakllari: Qo‘noqxoja, Qonoqqul

properties.name: Qo‘ng‘irboy, Qo‘ng‘ir
properties.meaning: Qo‘ng‘ir sochli yoki qo‘ng‘ir kozli bola yoki Qongirot (qar) ismining qisqargan shakli

properties.name: Qo‘ng‘irot
properties.meaning: Qo‘ng‘irot qabilasiga mansub bola, qo‘ng‘irot farzandi

properties.name: Qo‘riqboy
properties.meaning: Qo‘riqlangan, himoyalangan bola yoki bo‘z bola

properties.name: Qo‘rchiboy
properties.meaning: Alloh saqlasin, asrasin, ya’ni ko‘rchilasin yoki sog‘ ulg‘ayib askar, qo‘riqchi bolsin

properties.name: Qo‘rqmas
properties.meaning: Mard, jasur, dovyurak

properties.name: Qo‘rg‘on, Qo‘rg‘onboy
properties.meaning: Qo‘rg‘ondek mahkam, mustahkam bo‘lsin yoki himoyalangan, muhofazalangan bola

properties.name: Qo‘chchi
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘shchi yoki g‘ochchi

properties.name: Qo‘chqor
properties.meaning: Peshonasi do‘ng yoki moyagi kattaroq bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola yohud sog‘ ulgayib qochqordek kuchli yigit bolsin. Shakllari: Qochqorbek, Qochqorboy

properties.name: Qo‘chqorali
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘chqor va Ali

properties.name: Qo‘chqorqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘chqor (Qo‘chqor+qul)

properties.name: Qo‘sha
properties.meaning: Badanida qo‘shaloq belgilar bilan tug‘ilgan bola yoki Qo‘shali tipli ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qo‘shali
properties.meaning: Otasiga yoki oldingi farzandlarga qo‘shilsin va Ali o‘z panohida asrasin, yohud qar. Xushali

properties.name: Qo‘shan
properties.meaning: Qo‘shnazar, Qo‘shniyoz (Xushnazar, Xushniyoz) kabi ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Qo‘shar, Qo‘sharboy
properties.meaning: Alloh ota-onasiga yoki oldingi bolalarga qo‘shar, sog‘u omon ulg‘ayar deb umid qilamiz

properties.name: Qo‘shbaxt
properties.meaning: Qo‘shaloq, ulkan baxt sohibi yoki qar. Xushbaxt

properties.name: Qo‘shbek, Qo‘shboy
properties.meaning: Bolalar safiga qo‘shilsin, yashasin yoki qar. Xushbek, Xushboy

properties.name: Qo‘shbosh
properties.meaning: Boshi qo‘sh bo‘lsin, o‘lmasin, yashab ketsin

properties.name: Qo‘shboq
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushvaqt

properties.name: Qo‘shboqbuvi
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushvaqt

properties.name: Qo‘shbo‘ta
properties.meaning: Bo‘tadek suyukli (bo‘taloq) o‘g‘il ulgayib kattalar safiga qoshilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shvaqt
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushvaqt

properties.name: Qo‘shvoq
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushvaqt

properties.name: Qo‘shdavlat
properties.meaning: Qo‘sh boylik, qo‘shaloq baxt bo‘lgan bola yoki qar. Xushdavlat

properties.name: Qo‘shjon
properties.meaning: Qo‘sh so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlarning eq.shakli yoki oldingi bolalar safiga qo‘shilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shim
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘shmuhammad

properties.name: Qo‘shinboy
properties.meaning: Otasi yoki akasi armiyada bo‘lganda tug‘ilgan bola yoki kuchli, qudratli, jasur

properties.name: Qo‘shmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘shmuhammad

properties.name: Qo‘shmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Qo‘shmuhammad

properties.name: Qo‘shmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushmirza yoki bu bola sog‘ bo‘lib oldingi bolalar, o‘z tengdoshlariga qo‘shilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shmon
properties.meaning: Qo‘sh, (xush) so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi qo‘shma ismlarning eq.shaki

properties.name: Qo‘shmoq, Qo‘shmoqboy
properties.meaning: Ota-onasi turli millardan bo‘lgan oila farzandi; metis bola

properties.name: Qo‘shmurod
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushmurod yoki bola ulg‘ayib o‘zidan avvalgi bolalarga yoki o‘z tengdoshlariga qo‘shilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shmuhammad
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushmuhammad yoki bola sog‘ ulg‘ayib o‘zgalar safiga qo‘shilsin va Muhammad (sav) uni oz panohida asrasin

properties.name: Qo‘shnazar
properties.meaning: Qar. Xushnazar

properties.name: Qo‘shniyoz
properties.meaning: Allohdan iltijolar qilib olingan bola ulg‘ayib kattalar safida qo‘shilsin yoki qar. Xushniyoz

properties.name: Qo‘shoq
properties.meaning: Badanida qandaydir ortiqcha, belgi bilan (qul yoki oyog‘ida qo‘shimcha barmoqcha yoki boshqa xil xususiyatlar) tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qo‘shpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Po‘latdek mustahkam bo‘lsin va sog‘ ulg‘ayib ozgalar safiga qoshilsin yoki qar. Xushpolat

properties.name: Qo‘shtan
properties.meaning: Badanida biror bir ortiqcha, g‘ayritabiiy belgi bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qo‘shtirak
properties.meaning: Bola sog‘ ulg‘ayib ota-onasiga suyanch, ko‘makchi bo‘lsin

properties.name: Qo‘shtoy
properties.meaning: Erkatoy, suyukli o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib o‘zgalar safiga qoshilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shchi, Qo‘shchiboy
properties.meaning: Dalaga qo‘sh chiqqanda tug‘ilgan bola yoki sog‘ ulg‘ayib boshqa tengdoshlari safiga qoshilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shsha
properties.meaning: Ikki barmog‘i qo‘shilib, bir-biriga yopishib turgan holda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qo‘shyurak
properties.meaning: Qo‘sh yurakli, jasur, botir, dovyurak

properties.name: Qo‘shqin, Qo‘shqinboy
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib o‘zgalar safiga qo‘shilsin

properties.name: Qo‘shqul
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib o‘zgalar safiga qo‘shilsin yoki qar. Xushqul

properties.name: Qo‘qon, Qo‘qonboy
properties.meaning: Qo‘qon shahrida yoki otasi Qo‘qonga ketganda (yoki kelganda) tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qadambu
properties.meaning: Qadami qutlug‘ qiz

properties.name: Qadrbeka
properties.meaning: Izzat-e’tiborga loyiq, oliy nasab qiz

properties.name: Qadriya
properties.meaning: E’zozli, mo‘tabar qiz

properties.name: Qaymoq
properties.meaning: Shirin, suyukli yoki badanida ortiq belgi (xol, ortiqcha barmoq, biror nishon) bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Qaynaroy
properties.meaning: Sho‘x, jo‘shqin, g‘ayratli qiz

properties.name: Qayril
properties.meaning: Burilgan, yaxshilik tomonga qayrilsin. Bu ism bolaning sog‘ayib ketishini yoki navbatdagi bola o‘g‘il bo‘lishini orzu qilishni ifoda qiladi

properties.name: Sayidjo‘ra

properties.name: Sayidikrom

properties.name: Sayidislom
properties.meaning: Shariatning (islomning) rahnamosi, peshvosi; islom yo‘liga boshlovchi

properties.name: Sayidkamol

properties.name: Sayidmurod

properties.name: Sayidmuhammad

properties.name: Sayidnabi

properties.name: Sayidnazar

properties.name: Sayidota

properties.name: Sayidoxun

properties.name: Sayidrasul

properties.name: Sayidrahmon
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Rahmon

properties.name: Sayidrizo

properties.name: Sayidsulton
properties.meaning: Diniy peshvolarning sardori, sultoni

properties.name: Sayidtemir

properties.name: Sayidto‘g‘on
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va To‘g‘on

properties.name: Sayidumar
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Umar

properties.name: Sayidusmon
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Usmon

properties.name: Sayidfozil

properties.name: Sayideson

properties.name: Sayidyax’yo
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Yax’yo

properties.name: Sayidya’qub

properties.name: Sayidg‘affor

properties.name: Sayidg‘ozi

properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Hasan

properties.name: Sayidhoji
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Hoji

properties.name: Sayidhusayn
properties.meaning: Qar. Sayid va Husayn

properties.name: Sayir

properties.name: Sayis

properties.name: Sayfan

properties.meaning: Tanlangan, saylab olingan; omadli yoki qilich, shamshir. Asli: Sayfiddin, Sayfulla

properties.name: Sayfiali

properties.name: Sayfiddin

properties.name: Sayfulislom

properties.name: Sayfulmalik

properties.name: Sayfulmulk

properties.name: Sayqal

properties.name: Sayg‘aq

properties.meaning: Oiladagi sakkizinchi o‘g‘il, sakkizinchi farzandi

properties.name: Sakson
properties.meaning: Otasi sakson yoshligida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il yoki sog‘ ulgayib saksonga kirsin. Shakllari: Saksonboy, Saksonmirza

properties.name: Saksonmurod
properties.meaning: Otasi sakson yoshligida tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin yoki otasi sakson yoshligida erishilgan orzu, umid

properties.meaning: Qar. Sarson va To‘ra

properties.name: Saktosh

properties.name: Salavatulla

properties.name: Salimnazar

properties.name: Salomqul

properties.name: Samadali

properties.name: Samadmirza

properties.name: Samadturdi

properties.name: Samariddin
properties.meaning: Dinning mevasi, din baxsh etgan bola; dinning sovg‘asi, ehsoni yoki dinga foyda, naf keltirayotgan bola

properties.name: Sami

properties.name: Samim

properties.name: Samin
properties.meaning: Qadrli, aziz, qimmatli. Shakllari: Saminboy, Saminjon

properties.name: Samir

properties.name: Samit
properties.meaning: Sokin, osoyishta, osuda

properties.name: Sangarboy

properties.name: Sangbas

properties.name: Sangzor

properties.name: Sanginmirza

properties.name: Sanginmurod

properties.name: Sangmuhammad

properties.name: Sanjar
properties.meaning: Aynan: Sanchmoq, pichoq bilan urmoq; shiddatli, o‘tkir, kuchli yoki qal’a, qo‘rg‘on, yohud g‘olib muzaffar

properties.name: Sanjarmirza

properties.name: Sanjartilla
properties.meaning: Shiddatkor, o‘tkir va tilladek qimmatli bola

properties.name: Sanjarqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Sanjar (Sanjar+qul)

properties.name: Sanzor
properties.meaning: Qar. Sangzor

properties.name: Sano
properties.meaning: Madh, maqtov, tahsin, shukronalar aytish asli: Sanoulla

properties.name: Sanoat

properties.name: Sanoatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning ko‘rkam, go‘zal bandasi, Allohning ko‘rkam, hunarlar sohibi bo‘lgan bandasi

properties.name: Sanor, Sanorboy
properties.meaning: Loy; balchiq; yomon, iflos. Bolani yomon ko‘zdan asrash uhcun beriluvchi ism

properties.name: Sanoulla
properties.meaning: Allohga minnatdorchilik bildiruvchi shukronalar aytuvchi bola

properties.name: Sanoxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Sano, Sanoulla. Asli: Sanoulxo‘ja yoki xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan maqtovga loyiq bola

properties.name: Sanoqul
properties.meaning: Allohning madh etuvchi, olqishlovchi, unga shukronalar qiluvchi

properties.name: San’at

properties.name: San’atilla, San’atulla

properties.name: Saodat
properties.meaning: Baxtli, iqbolli, baxtiyor

properties.name: Saodatali

properties.name: Saodatbek

properties.name: Saodatvali
properties.meaning: Qar. Saodat va Vali

properties.name: Saodatnur

properties.name: Saodatulla

properties.name: Saodatqul
properties.meaning: Baxtli, iqbolli qul, banda yoki Muhammad (sav) avlodlarning xizmatkori, quli

properties.name: Saraboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Sarabek

properties.name: Sarbaland
properties.meaning: Baxtiyor, boshi osmonga yetgan, omadli, mag‘rur yoki to‘siq, to‘g‘on; himoyalangan, mustahkam

properties.name: Sarboz
properties.meaning: Askar, soldat, harbiy xizmatkor

properties.name: Sarboy

properties.name: Sarbola
properties.meaning: Oiladagi bosh bola yoki mahkam, chidamli bola

properties.name: Sarvar
properties.meaning: Yo‘lboshchi, boshliq, rahnamo

properties.name: Sarvariddin
properties.meaning: Din yo‘liga yetaklovchi, rahnamo yoki dinchilar, musulmonlarining rahbari, sarvari

properties.name: Sarvarniso
properties.meaning: Ayollarning sardori, yo‘lboshchisi; ayollarning eng donosi, aqllisi

properties.name: Sarvat
properties.meaning: Boy, badavlat, risqu ro‘zli, mol-dunyosi ko‘p yoki Sarvad - qo‘shiq, doston, ya’ni shodon, baxtiyor

properties.name: Sardor

properties.name: Sardorxon
properties.meaning: Aynan: Xonlarning boshlig‘i, peshvosi, rahnamosi yoki qar. Sardor (Sardor+xon)

properties.name: Sardorqul
properties.meaning: Lashkarboshi, yo‘lboshchining xizmatchisi, quli

properties.name: Sari
properties.meaning: Aynan: Sariq rangli bola, sariq sochli bola yoki taniqli, mashhur; oqsuyaklar, aslzodalar avlodiga mansub

properties.name: Sariali
properties.meaning: Qar. Sari va Ali

properties.name: Saribek

properties.name: Sevinchbonu

properties.name: Yozdonqul

properties.name: Yaxshimamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Yaxshimuhammad

properties.name: Yaxshimat
properties.meaning: Qar. Yaxshimuhammad

properties.name: Yaxshimirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Yaxshi va Mirza

properties.name: Yaxshimurod
properties.meaning: Maqbul, munosib bola ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

properties.name: Yaxshimuhammad
properties.meaning: Muhammad - yaxshi, a’lodir yoki munosib, maqbul bolani Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Yaxshinazar
properties.meaning: Allohning lutfi, iltifoti tufayli erishilgan maqbul, orzu qilingan bola

properties.name: Yaxshiniyoz
properties.meaning: Allohdan o‘tinib so‘rab olingan maqbul, munosib bola yoki Allohning tuhfasi, sovg‘asi

properties.name: Yaxshinor
properties.meaning: Badanida xosiyatli, munosib xol bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Yaxshisoat
properties.meaning: Xosiyatli, qutlug‘ soatda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Yaxshitoy
properties.meaning: Munosib, maqbul hamda erka, suyukli o‘g‘il

properties.name: Yaxshiulla
properties.meaning: Allohning maqbul, munosib bandasi

properties.name: Yaxshiqul
properties.meaning: Allohning munosib, maqbul bandasi, quli

properties.name: Yashar
properties.meaning: Yashaydigan, barhayot bo‘ladigan umri uzoq bola. Shakllari: Yasharbek, Yasharboy, Yasharqul

properties.name: Yashin
properties.meaning: Chaqmoqli tunda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Yashnar
properties.meaning: Gullab yashnaydigan, umri barq uruvchi, barhayot bo‘luvchi

properties.name: Ya’qub
properties.meaning: o‘kcha tovon, izidan boruvchi, ergashuvchi. Bibliyadagi afsonaga ko‘ra, egizak bola tug‘ilgan bo‘lib, ikkinchisi birinchi tugilgan akasidan qolib ketmaslik uchun tovodidan ushlab yurgan emish. Bu nom paygambarlardan biri ismi (Yakov)ning arabcha shaklidir. U Yusuf (qar.) ning otasi hisoblanadai

properties.name: Yaqin, Yaqinjon
properties.meaning: Haqiqiy, muqarrar, aniq

properties.name: Yahyo, Yah’yo
properties.meaning: o‘ta saxiy, muruvvatli, ochiq qo‘l; yashovchi, barhayot, hayotiy yoki xushxulq, insonga do‘st. Payg‘ambarlardan birining nomi

properties.name: Yahyopo‘lat
properties.meaning: Qar. Yahyo va Po‘lat

properties.name: Yahyoxun
properties.meaning: Qar. Yahyo (Yahyo+xon)

properties.name: Yahyoqul
properties.meaning: Yahyo payg‘ambarga tobe, uning sodiq xizmatkori

properties.name: Yetar
properties.meaning: Hadeb qiz tug‘ilavergan oilalarda, endi qiz tug‘ilishi yetar, keyingisi o‘g‘il bolsin degan ma’noda beriladi

properties.name: Yetarqul
properties.meaning: Gul, ya’ni qizlar tug‘ilishi yetar, keyingisi o‘g‘il bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yetaroy
properties.meaning: Oy, ya’ni qizlar tug‘ilishi yetar, navbatdagisi o‘g‘il bo‘lsin. Yetar (Yetar+oy)

properties.name: Yetmishoy
properties.meaning: Otasi yetmiz yoshligida tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: Yetmishxon
properties.meaning: Otasi yetmish yoshligida tug‘ilgan qadrli, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Yobonoy
properties.meaning: Cho‘lda (yovonda) tug‘ilgan qiz yoki murodimiz hosil bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Yodgora
properties.meaning: Tug‘ilgandan keyin ota (yoki onasi) vafot etgan, ulardan yodgor bo‘lib qolgan qiz

properties.name: Yodgorbibi
properties.meaning: Onasidan yodgor bo‘lib qolgan qiz, ulg‘ayib, baland martabalar sohibi bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yodgorgul
properties.meaning: Onasidn yodgor bo‘lib qolgan, go‘zal, zebo qiz

properties.name: Yodgoroy
properties.meaning: Onasidan yodgor bo‘lib qolgan oydek suluv qiz

properties.name: Yodgorxon
properties.meaning: Onasidan yodgor bo‘lib qolgan qadrli, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Yodgorqiz
properties.meaning: Vafot etgan onasidan yodgor bo‘lgan, onasining qo‘zi bo‘lmish qizi

properties.name: Yozbeka
properties.meaning: Yozda tug‘ilgan va beklar avlodiga mansub qiz

properties.name: Yozbibi
properties.meaning: Yoz (bahor)da tug‘ilgan martabali, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Yozbika
properties.meaning: Qar. Yozbeka

properties.name: Yozgul
properties.meaning: Yoz (ko‘klam)da tug‘ilgan go‘zal qiz yoki ko‘klam chechagi

properties.name: Yozjamol
properties.meaning: Yozda tug‘ilgan sohibjamol qiz

properties.name: Yozjannat
properties.meaning: Yozda tavallud topgan va jannatga mansub qiz

properties.name: Yozjon
properties.meaning: Yoz (ko‘klam)da tug‘ilgan aziz, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Yozchechak
properties.meaning: Ko‘klam, bahorda ochilgan gul, ya’ni bahor guldek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Yolqina
properties.meaning: Nurli, yolqinli, otashin qiz

properties.name: Yombixon
properties.meaning: Yombi (tilla yoki kumush quyilmasi) kabi qimmatli, bebaho qiz

properties.name: Yomg‘iroy
properties.meaning: Yomg‘ir yog‘gan kuni tug‘ilgan oydek suluv qiz yoki yomg‘irdek serob bolsin (Yomgir+oy)

properties.name: Yora
properties.meaning: Bilaguzuk, ya’ni bilaguzukdek mahkam va etiborli qiz

properties.name: Yorqinoy
properties.meaning: Hayoti nurli va oydek suluv qiz yoki oydek suluv, mehribon, dilkash qiz

properties.name: Yosuman
properties.meaning: Yosuman guldek chiroyli, zebo qiz

properties.name: Yoqut
properties.meaning: Qizil rangli qimmatbaho tosh, yoqut (Ã¯Â¿Â½Ã¯Â¿Â½Ã¯Â¿Â½Ã¯Â¿Â½Ã¯Â¿Â½). Turkiy xalqlar yoqut kishini turli kasalliklardan asraydi, davo bo‘ldi deb hisoblashgan

properties.name: Yoqutbibi
properties.meaning: Yoqutdek bebaho, nodir qiz, yoqutdek chiroyli qiz

properties.name: Yoqutoy
properties.meaning: Yoqutdek suluv, bebaho, nodir va oydek qiz

properties.name: Yoqutxon
properties.meaning: Yoqutdek nodir va baland martabali, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Yigitoy
properties.meaning: Yigitlardek jasur, mard qiz bo‘lib o‘ssin yoki keyingi bola o‘g‘il bolsin

properties.name: Yo‘lbuvi
properties.meaning: Yo‘l (safar)da tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: Yo‘ldoshbu, Yo‘ldoshbuvi
properties.meaning: Otasiga (oldingi aka-opalariga do‘st, hamroh bo‘lib yursin

properties.name: Yo‘ldoshoy
properties.meaning: Ota-onasiga hamroh, esh bo‘lib yuruvchi va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Yo‘ldoshxon
properties.meaning: Ota-onasiga hamroh, esh bo‘lib yuruvchi, qadrli, baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Yo‘llibeka
properties.meaning: Yo‘lda (safarda) tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: Yuzbeka
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib yuzga kirsin va ulug‘ martabali bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yuzlibeka
properties.meaning: Pardali bo‘lib tug‘ilgan qiz. Sol: Parda, Pardagul

properties.name: Yuzliqo
properties.meaning: Yuzi berkilgan holda, pardali bo‘lib tug‘ilgan qiz

properties.name: Yulduz
properties.meaning: Tolei yulduzdek yuksak va porloq bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Yulduzxon, Yulduzoy

properties.name: Yulduzxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Yulduz (Yulduz+xon)

properties.name: Yunusoy
properties.meaning: Qar. Yunus (Yunus+oy)

properties.name: Yunuspari
properties.meaning: Yunus payg‘ambarning xizmatkori, quli

properties.name: Yursin
properties.meaning: Sog‘u salomat yursin, ulg‘aysin; Shakllari: Yursinbek, Yursinboy, Yursinoy, Yursinxon

properties.name: Yayra
properties.meaning: Hur, ozod, yayrab o‘ssin

properties.name: Yayrasin
properties.meaning: Yayrab, quvnab o‘ssin

properties.name: Yangigul
properties.meaning: Toza, pokiza, yashnagan gul

properties.name: Yangil
properties.meaning: Yanglishsin, adashsin, ya’ni navbatdagi farzand o‘g‘il bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Yangiljon, Yangilbot

properties.name: Yangiloy
properties.meaning: Oydek suluv qizdan keyingisi o‘g‘il bo‘lsin; yanglishsin, almashsin

properties.name: Yangisuluv
properties.meaning: Toza, pokiza, hamda zebo qiz

properties.name: Yarashgul
properties.meaning: Qar. Yarash (Yarash+gul)

properties.name: Yarashiq
properties.meaning: Arziydigan, loyiq; yarashiqli, kelishgan

properties.name: Yatim, Yarimgul
properties.meaning: Yakka, tanho, yagona; tengsiz yoki yetim, sag‘ir bola

properties.name: Yatima
properties.meaning: Yakka, tanho qiz yoki yetim qiz

properties.name: Yaxshigul
properties.meaning: Qizlarning yaxshisi, a’losi

properties.name: Yaxshiqiz
properties.meaning: Durust, munosib qiz

properties.name: Yashil
properties.meaning: Yarashiqli, go‘zal, zebo

properties.name: Yashna
properties.meaning: Umri yashnasin, barq ursin, farovon yashasin

properties.name: Yashnargul
properties.meaning: Hayoti gul kabi yashnoq, go‘zal va farovon bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yashnaroy
properties.meaning: Gulday go‘zal qizning hayoti yashnagan va farovon bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yashnasin
properties.meaning: Gullasin, hayoti farovon va qutli bo‘lsin

properties.name: Yashnaxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Yashna (Yashna+xon)

properties.name: Zabar
properties.meaning: Baland, yuqori turuvchi, baland martabali

properties.name: Zabardast
properties.meaning: Kuchli, qudratli; mohir, uddaburon

properties.name: Zabiy
properties.meaning: Ohu, erkak ohu

properties.name: Zabir
properties.meaning: Mahkam, mustahkam; to‘silgan, himoya qilingan; kuchli, qudratli

properties.name: Zabirulla
properties.meaning: Alloh o‘zi panohiga olgan bola yoki Allohning kuchli, qudratli bandasi

properties.name: Zabih
properties.meaning: Qar. Zabihulla

properties.name: Zabihulla
properties.meaning: Allohga atalgan, sadaqa qilingan o‘g‘il. Allohga o‘zini bag‘ishlagan bola

properties.name: Zabonboy
properties.meaning: Biyron, so‘zga chechan o‘g‘il yoki yolqinli, nurli bola

properties.name: Zabriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning himoyasichi yoki dinni saqlovchi, asrovchi bola

properties.name: Zabunboy
properties.meaning: Arzimas, ojiz, bechorahol bola. Chaqaloqqa ko‘z tegmasin, u e’tiborsiz bo‘lsin deb berilgan ism

properties.name: Zabur
properties.meaning: Yozilgan, bitilgan. Dovud payg‘ambarning diniy kitobi nomi

properties.name: Zavurboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Zabur (Zabur+boy)

properties.name: Zavqi
properties.meaning: Xursand, shodon, baxtiyor. Zavqiddin (qar.) ismining eq. Shakllari: Zavqibek, Zavqijon

properties.name: Zavqiddin
properties.meaning: Din beruvchi shavq, lazzat, shodlik yoki dinning huzur-halovatli farzandi

properties.name: Zavqli, Zavqlibek
properties.meaning: Shodlik, quvonch hamroh bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Zayd
properties.meaning: Tuhfa, in’om yoki ko‘payish, qo‘shilish. Qar. Zaydulla

properties.name: Zaydali
properties.meaning: Ali in’om, ehson qilgan o‘g‘il

properties.name: Zaydalim
properties.meaning: Alim (qar.), ya’ni biluvchi, dono (Alloh) bergan ehson, tuhfa

properties.name: Zaydbek
properties.meaning: Alloh ato qilgan va beklar nasliga mansub bola

properties.name: Zaydi
properties.meaning: Zayd so‘zi bilan boshlangan ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Zaydulla
properties.meaning: Allohning in’omi, ehsoni, himmati

properties.name: Zaylob
properties.meaning: Qar. Zaylobiddin. Sol: Zaynab

properties.name: Zaylobiddin
properties.meaning: Qar. Zaynulobiddin. Sol: Zaynobiddin

properties.name: Zaymiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning yo‘lboshchisi, rahnamosi, din sardori

properties.name: Zaynabiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning go‘zalligi, diniy nafost yoki dinning ko‘rkli farzandi

properties.name: Zaynabmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Zaynab va Mirza

properties.name: Zaynabxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan ko‘rkam bola

properties.name: Zaynal
properties.meaning: Zaynulobiddin (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

properties.name: Zayni
properties.meaning: Zayniddin (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

properties.name: Zayniali
properties.meaning: Ali ato qilgan ko‘rkam o‘g‘il yoki ko‘rkam ogilni Ali panohida asrasin

properties.name: Zaynibashar
properties.meaning: Kishilarning, insonlarning eng ko‘rkami, go‘zali

properties.name: Zayniddin
properties.meaning: Dinning ko‘rki, bezagi, diniy nafosat  yoki dinning ko‘rki bo‘luvchi bola

properties.name: Zayniqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Zayni (Zayni+qul)

properties.name: Zaynulislom
properties.meaning: Islomning bezagi, ko‘rki

properties.name: Zaynulla
properties.meaning: Allohning go‘zal, ko‘hlik bandasi

properties.name: Zaynulobiddin
properties.meaning: Dinga sig‘inuvchilar (xudojo‘ylar)ning eng a’losi, go‘zali. Bu nom imom Alining faxriy unvoni bo‘lgan va oldin shiitlar, keyinchalik esa sunniylar orasida kishi ismi sifatida tarqalgan

properties.name: Zayriddin
properties.meaning: Asli Zayniddin (qar.) bo‘lsa kerak. Eht.: Zohiriddin (qar.)

properties.name: Zayfulla
properties.meaning: Alloh yuborgan mehmon, Alloh ato qilgan bola

properties.name: Zakariya
properties.meaning: Zaxariya - Allohni yodda tutuvchi, Allohning xotirasi yoki er, mard, jasur

properties.name: Zaki, Zakiboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Zakiy, Zakiulla

properties.name: Zakiy
properties.meaning: Aqlli, zukko, tezfahm, sezgir, ziyrak

properties.name: Zakiulla
properties.meaning: Allohning sezgir, zukko bandasi yoki Allohning ozoda, pokiza bandasi

properties.name: Zakoulla
properties.meaning: Allohning topqirligi, zakovati, donoligi yoki Allohning aqlli, dono bandasi

properties.name: Zalil
properties.meaning: Tuban, past; bechora, faqir, gadoy. Ota-ona o‘zlarining farzandga muhtoj bo‘lganini shunday ifodalaydi

properties.name: Zamzamali
properties.meaning: Qar. Zamzam va Ali

properties.name: Zamir
properties.meaning: Yurak, qalb, vijdon. Asli: Zamiriddin (qar.)

properties.name: Zamiriddin
properties.meaning: Dinning yuragi, qalbi; dinga sodiqlik bilan vijdonan sig‘inuvchi

properties.name: Zamon
properties.meaning: Davri, zamonasining munosib farzandi. Shakllari: Zamonbek, Zamonboy, Zamonqul

properties.name: Zamonali
properties.meaning: Qar. Zamon va Ali yoki davrining munosib farzandini imom Ali qo‘llab yursin

properties.name: Zamonberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh davriga, zamonasiga munosib o‘g‘il ato qildi

properties.name: Zamonbibi
properties.meaning: Zamonasining muhtarama qizi

properties.name: Zamonkeldi
properties.meaning: Zamonasi, davriga munosib o‘g‘il tug‘ildi

properties.name: Zamonmirza
properties.meaning: Davrining o‘qimishli, martabali o‘g‘li

properties.name: Zamonmurod
properties.meaning: Davri, zamonasining murod-maqsadli farzandi

properties.name: Zamontoy
properties.meaning: Zamonasining munosib va suyukli hurmatli farzandi

properties.name: Zamonxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Davrining xo‘jalar nasliga mansub bo‘lgan munosib farzandi

properties.name: Zamonqul
properties.meaning: Davr, zamonasining munosib, sadoqatli xizmatkori bo‘lsin

properties.name: Zamcha
properties.meaning: Zamcha (qovun) pishganda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Zanbur
properties.meaning: Ari, qovoqari. Bolasi turmagan oilalarda shunday ism berishadi. Eht.: Zabur (qar.)

properties.name: Zangi
properties.meaning: Qoracha, qora bola yoki ko‘tariluvchi, yuksaluvchi; mahkam, mustahkam

properties.name: Zanjir, Zanjirboy
properties.meaning: Zanjirdek mahkam, mustahkam yoki otasi, akalariga zanjirdek bog‘lanib qolsin, yashasin

properties.name: Zanjirali
properties.meaning: Qar. Zanjir va Ali

properties.name: Zarasp
properties.meaning: Oq ot egasi, chavandoz, doro

properties.name: Zarbat, Zarbatbek
properties.meaning: Eht.: Zarbaft, Zarbof

properties.name: Zarbdor
properties.meaning: Ilg‘or, peshqadam, yangi davrda ijod qilingan ism

properties.name: Zargar
properties.meaning: Tillo buyumlar ustasi

properties.name: Zargarxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan bola ulg‘ayib tillakor usta bo‘lsin

properties.name: Zariddin
properties.meaning: Dinning tillodek bebaho, a’lo bolasi; dinning sodiq xizmatkori, sodiq xudojo‘y

properties.name: Zarirxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Qar. Zarir va Xo‘ja

properties.name: Zarif
properties.meaning: Pok, toza, pokiza, nozikfahm, ziyrak; aqlli, dono. Shakllari: Zarifboy, Zarifjon

properties.name: Zarifiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning pokiza, zukko farzandi

properties.name: Zarifulla
properties.meaning: Allohning chiroyli yoki aql-zakovatli bandasi

properties.name: Zarifxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan pokiza yoki zukko bola

properties.name: Zarifqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Zarif (Zarif+Qul)

properties.name: Zarifkeldi
properties.meaning: Qimmatli, qadrli o‘g‘il tug‘ildi

properties.name: Zarmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Zarmuhammad

properties.name: Zarqalam
properties.meaning: Qizil qalam, tilla qalam

properties.name: Zarqora
properties.meaning: Zardek qimmatli va jasur, qudratli bola

properties.name: Zarqori
properties.meaning: Qar. Zar va Qori

properties.name: Zarqul
properties.meaning: Allohning qadrli, e’zozli bandasi, quli

properties.name: Zarg‘am
properties.meaning: Zirg‘am-arslon, sher; jasur, qo‘rqmas, dovyurak

properties.name: Zafar
properties.meaning: g‘olib, muzaffar; baxtli, saodatli. Shakllari: Zafarbek, Zafarjon

properties.name: Zafariddin
properties.meaning: Dinning zafari, g‘olibligi; dinning iqboli, istiqboli

properties.name: Zafaroy
properties.meaning: g‘olib, yengilmas va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

properties.name: Za’faron
properties.meaning: Za’faron guldek ko‘rkam yoki yoqut toshdek qimmatli, nurli

properties.name: Zafarxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan baxtli, toleli baland bola

properties.name: Zafir
properties.meaning: g‘olib keluvchi, yenguvchi

properties.name: Zahiriddin
properties.meaning: Nurli, ravshan, chehrasidan nur yog‘iluvchi yoki dinning posboni, himoyachisi

properties.name: Zahirulla
properties.meaning: Allohning nuri, yog‘dusi yoki Allohning panohida bo‘lgan bola

properties.name: Zahob,  Zahab
properties.meaning: Tilladek bebaho, qadrli (oltin)

properties.name: Ziyo
properties.meaning: Nurli, ravshan, yorqin yoki baxtli, tolei baland yoki ziyo so‘zi bilan boshlanadigan qo‘shma ismlar (Ziyobuddin, Ziyoali, Ziyodulla) eq.shakli

properties.name: Ziyoahmad
properties.meaning: Ahmadning (Muhammad (sav)) nuri, ziyosi. Sol: Ziyomuhammad yoki Muhammadning muruvvati,tuhfasi

properties.name: Ziyoali
properties.meaning: Alining mehri, muruvvati tufayli erishilgan o‘g‘il yoki Alining tuhfasi, in’omi

properties.name: Ziyovuddin
properties.meaning: Dinning nuri, yog‘dusi, din mash’ali yoki dinning muruvvati, ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan bola

properties.name: Ziyod
properties.meaning: Umri ziyoda, farovon bo‘lsin yoki badanida qandaydir ortiqcha belgisi bilan tug‘ilgan bola. Shakllari: Ziyodbek, Ziyodjon

properties.name: Ziyodatulla
properties.meaning: Alloh umrini ziyoda, ortiq qilib bergan farzand

properties.name: Ziyodulla
properties.meaning: Alloh bergan ehson, tuhfa. Alloh umrini uzoq qilib bergan bola

properties.name: Ziyodxol
properties.meaning: Uzoq umrli hamda xosiyatli xol bilan tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Ziyodqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyod va Qo‘zi

properties.name: Ziyoviddin
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyovuddin

properties.name: Ziyom, Ziyomboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyomiddin

properties.name: Ziyomat
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyomuhammad

properties.name: Ziyomiddin
properties.meaning: Dinning boyligi, davlati yoki dinning boy, badavlat kishisi

properties.name: Ziyomxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodidan bo‘lgan, boy, badavlat bola

properties.name: Ziyor
properties.meaning: Ziyoratchi, muqaddas joylar, avliyolarga sig‘inuvchi yoki hoji

properties.name: Ziyorat
properties.meaning: Muqaddas joylarga sig‘inib, ziyorat qilib erishilgan bola

properties.name: Ziyoriddin, Ziyoratdin
properties.meaning: Dinga amal qiluvchi, sig‘inuvchi; hoji

properties.name: Ziyouddin
properties.meaning: Dinning nuri, mash’ali. Bu nom o‘rta asrlarda bazi hukmron va ruhoniylarning faxriy laqabi bo‘lgan. Sol: Ziyovuddin

properties.name: Ziyoxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan nurli, baxtu iqbolli bola

properties.name: Ziyoqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyo (Ziyo+qul)

properties.name: Ziyoqo‘zi
properties.meaning: Qar. Ziyo va Qo‘zi

properties.name: Ziyohiddin
properties.meaning: Eht.: Ziyovuddin (qar.)

properties.name: Ziynat
properties.meaning: Bezangan, orolangan go‘zal, chiroyli. Shakllari: Ziynatbu, Ziynatoy, Ziynatxon

properties.name: Zynatulla
properties.meaning: Allohning chiroyli, yaxshi bandasi; Allohning yaxshi xislatlarga ega kishisi

properties.name: Zikir
properties.meaning: Yodlash, xotirlash. So‘fiylar, darveshlarning Allohni yodga olib zikr tutishi. Asli: Zikirulla (qar.)

properties.name: Zikirali
properties.meaning: Alini yodga oluvchi, xotirlovchi yoki xudojo‘y bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Zikriyo,  Zikiriyo
properties.meaning: Allohni eslovchi, xotirlovchi, ulug‘lovchi; darvesh, qalandar

properties.name: Zikriyoqul
properties.meaning: Allohni xotirlovchi, Alloh yodi bilan yashovchi

properties.name: Zikrilla
properties.meaning: Allohning yodi, xotirasi; Allohni eslovchi, yoz etuvchi kishi; xudojo‘y

properties.name: Zilolboy
properties.meaning: Pokiza, halol bola yoki muhofaza qilingan, himoyalangan bola

properties.name: Zilulla
