properties.meaning: Qar. Chegaboy

properties.name: Chekboy
properties.meaning: Bog‘langan, ulangan; tutashgan, ya’ni mahkam, mustahkam

properties.name: Chekmirza
properties.meaning: Qar. Chekboy

properties.name: Cherikboy
properties.meaning: Qo‘shin, lashkar, askar. Harbiy yurishlar paytida tug‘ilgan bola yoki kuchli, qudratli, chidamli

properties.name: Cherikbosh
properties.meaning: Qo‘shin, lashkar boshlig‘I; qo‘mondon, lashkarboshi

properties.name: Chechan
properties.meaning: So‘zamol, chaqqon, uddaburon yoki notiq, shirintil

properties.name: Chehrazod
properties.meaning: Toza nasl farzand, aslzoda yoki go‘zal, zebo

properties.name: Chil, Chilboy
properties.meaning: Kulrang kaklik yoki bulduruq

properties.name: Chilan, Chilanboy
properties.meaning: Eht.: Chilangan (qar.) yoki qar. Chilon

properties.name: Chilangar
properties.meaning: Temirchi, usta

properties.name: Chilmamat
properties.meaning: Chil so‘zi bilan boshlangan ba’zi ismlarning eq.shakli

properties.name: Chilmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Chilmuhammad

properties.name: Chilon
properties.meaning: Chilon (chelon) daraxti, chilonjiydadek mustahkam. Eht.: Chilangar (qar.)

properties.name: Chilton
properties.meaning: Qirqta ajralmas ruh, arvoh yoki mustahkam chidamli, irodali

properties.name: Chimboy
properties.meaning: Chim (soz, ajriqzor) dek mahkam, mustahkam bola yoki  to‘silgan, himoyalangan yohud chimboy urug‘iga mansub bola. Eht.: Chinboy (qar.)

properties.name: Chimirboy
properties.meaning: Dadal, epchil, o‘tkir, topag‘on yoki pishiq, puxta

properties.name: Chimkent, Chimkanboy
properties.meaning: Chimkent shahri nomiga nisbatan berilgan ism

properties.name: Chimmat
properties.meaning: To‘silgan, yashirilgan, himoya qilingan. Eht.: Chinmat < Chinmuhammad (qar)

properties.name: Chinali
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri, halol, adolatli o‘g‘ilni Ali oz panohida asrasin yoki jingalak sochli bolani Ali oz panohida asrasin

properties.name: Chinberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh - rost, chin qilib bergan, umri uzoq bola

properties.name: Chinboy
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri, rostgo‘y, adolatli bola yoki qar. Chimboy

properties.name: Chingiz
properties.meaning: Buyuk, qudratli. Mashhur jahongir Chingizxon (1227 yili vafot etgan) nomiga nisbat berilgan ism

properties.name: Chingizxon
properties.meaning: Buyuk, qudratli xon. Qar. Chingiz

properties.name: Chindavlat
properties.meaning: Umrini rostakam uzoq qilib berilgan boylik, ya’ni bola

properties.name: Chindiyor
properties.meaning: o‘lkaning rost, haqiqiy, ya’ni umrini uzoq qilib berilgan farzand

properties.name: Chinjigit
properties.meaning: Rost, haqiqiy, umri bilan berilgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib rostgo‘y yigit bolsin yoki jingalak sochli

properties.name: Chinitosh
properties.meaning: Pok, pokiza  va toshdek mahkam bola

properties.name: Chiniqul
properties.meaning: Allohning pokiza, ozoda, begunoh bandasi

properties.name: Chinyigit
properties.meaning: Umrini to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan bola yoki ulg‘ayib haqiqiy yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Chinmirza
properties.meaning: Umri haqqoniy, to‘liq qilib berilgan bola ulg‘ayib mirzalardek yigit bo‘lsin

properties.name: Chinmurod
properties.meaning: Rostdan istalgan, orzu qilingan, qo‘msab kutilgan bola

properties.name: Chinmuhammad
properties.meaning: Umrini to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Chinni
properties.meaning: Pokiza, ozoda yoki quloqlarni kichkina bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola yohud umrini uzoq qilib berilgan bola

properties.name: Chinoz
properties.meaning: Chinozda yoki Chinozni ziyorat qilgach tug‘ilgan bola yohud chinoz urug‘iga mansub bola

properties.name: Chinor
properties.meaning: Chinordek basavlat va umri uzoq bo‘lsin yoki suyanchiq, ko‘makchi bola. Shakllari: Chinorboy, Chinorjon

properties.name: Chinorberdi
properties.meaning: Alloh chinordek uzoq umrli bola ato qilgi yoki Alloh bergan va chinor kabi umri uzoq bola

properties.name: Chinoq
properties.meaning: Qulog‘i kemtik yoki burishiq bo‘lib yohud qulog‘I kichkina bo‘lin tugilgan bola

properties.name: Chinpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Haqiqiy, sof po‘latdek mustahkam bola yoki umri to‘liq qilib berilgan po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Chintemir
properties.meaning: Umri to‘liq qilib berilgan temirdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Chinterak
properties.meaning: To‘g‘ri o‘sgan terak

properties.name: Chintoy
properties.meaning: Umri to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan suyukli, erkatoy bola

properties.name: Chinturdi
properties.meaning: Umrini to‘liq qilib berilgan o‘g‘il yashasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Chintursin
properties.meaning: Umri to‘liq qilib berilgan bola tursin, yashasin

properties.name: Chinxo‘ja
properties.meaning: Umri rost, to‘liq qilib berilgan xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

properties.name: Chincha
properties.meaning: Umri uzoq kenja, jajji bola

properties.name: Chinqora
properties.meaning: Umrini to‘liq qilib berilgan kuchli, qudratli bola

properties.name: Chinqul
properties.meaning: Allohning umri uzoq bandasi

properties.name: Chirmash
properties.meaning: Oiladagilarga yaqinlashgin, bog‘lanib, chirmashib olgin, ya’ni sog‘ bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Chirmashboy, Chirmashxon

properties.name: Chiroq
properties.meaning: Hayoti yorug‘, nurli bo‘lsin yoki orzu qilingan bola

properties.name: Chirog‘ali
properties.meaning: Alining iltifoti, nuri tufayli topilgan bola

properties.name: Chitboy
properties.meaning: Nozik tabiat, tabiatli bola

properties.name: Chig‘atoy
properties.meaning: Aynan: Bola yoki jasur, botir, nomuschan. Bu nom Chingizxonning ikkinchi o‘g‘il ismi bo‘lgan

properties.name: Chovdir, Chovdur
properties.meaning: Aynan: Ovoza, ya’ni mashhur, taniqli yoki chovdir (turkman urug‘i)lar orasida tug‘ilgan

properties.name: Chodir
properties.meaning: Kapada tug‘ilgan bola yoki pardali bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola. Sol: Pardaboy

properties.name: Chokar
properties.meaning: Xizmatkor; navkar yoki yovvosh, odobli, mo‘min-qobil

properties.name: Cholboy
properties.meaning: Buvasining nomi berilgan bola yoki burul ot (ko‘kish, xoldor ot) dek baquvvat bo‘lsin yohud tukli bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Choparboy
properties.meaning: Ulg‘ayib chopqillab yursin yoki yaxshi daraklar keltiruvchi, qutli bola bo‘lsin

properties.name: Chor, Chorboy
properties.meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi o‘g‘il (farzand) yoki kirli, iflos, yomon bola. Keyingi ma’noda ism bolani yomon ko‘zlardan asrash niyatida qoyiladi. Shakllari: Chorboy, Chortoy

properties.name: Chori
properties.meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi farzand yoki Choriyor ismining shakli

properties.name: Choriyor
properties.meaning: Aynan: To‘rt do‘st, maslakdosh. Bular xalifai barhaqlar (choriyorlar) Abu Bakr Siddiq, Umar, Usmon, Alilardir

properties.name: Chorikeldi
properties.meaning: Alloh ato qilgan to‘rtinchi o‘g‘il

properties.name: Chorimirza
properties.meaning: To‘rtinchi o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib mirzalardek bilimdon yigit bolsin

properties.name: Chorixo‘ja
properties.meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan to‘rtinchi o‘gil

properties.name: Choriqul
properties.meaning: Qar. Chori (Chori+qul)

properties.name: Choriqurbon
properties.meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan to‘rtinchi bola

properties.name: Chormuhammad
properties.meaning: Qar. Chor va Muhammad

properties.name: Chortoq, Chortoqboy
properties.meaning: Chortoqda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Chorshanba
properties.meaning: Chorshanba kuni tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Chorshanboy
properties.meaning: Qar. Chorshanba

properties.name: Chunon
properties.meaning: Intiq bo‘lib kutilgan bola. Shakllari: Chunonbek, Chunonboy, Chunontoy, Chunonqul

properties.name: Chunonmirza
properties.meaning: Intiq bo‘lib kutilgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib mirzolardek yigit bolsin

properties.name: Chust
properties.meaning: Aynan: Chaqqon, shay, mohir, zebo qiz mahkam, mustahkam yohud munosib, sazovor. Eht.: Chustda tug‘ilgan bola, Chust farzandi

properties.name: Chuchuk
properties.meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy; aziz, e’zozli

properties.name: Cho‘yon
properties.meaning: Qar. Cho‘yan

properties.name: Cho‘kish
properties.meaning: Cho‘kich (cho‘kish)dek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Cho‘lbosh
properties.meaning: Cho‘lda tavallud topgan to‘ng‘ich bola

properties.name: Cho‘limurod
properties.meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan bola ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin yoki cho‘lda erishilgan orzu, tilak

properties.name: Cho‘liq
properties.meaning: Cho‘ponning yordamchisi, kichik cho‘pn

properties.name: Cho‘lli, Cho‘lliboy
properties.meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Cho‘lmurod
properties.meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il sog ulgayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin yoki cholda erishilgan orzu, tilak

properties.name: Cho‘lpon
properties.meaning: Tong yulduzi, yorug‘ yulduz (Venera), ya’ni tolei baland, saodatli bola

properties.name: Cho‘lponqul
properties.meaning: Allohning tolei baland, saodatli bandasi, quli

properties.name: Cho‘ponqul
properties.meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib qo‘ychi, qo‘ychivon bolsin; mollari kop, boy-badavlat bolsin yoki bechora, xoksor bola. Keyingi ma’noda ism bolani yomon kozlardan asrashga qaratilgan

properties.name: Cho‘rtanboy
properties.meaning: Cho‘rtan baliqdek erkin, yashovchan bo‘lsin

properties.name: Cho‘tboy
properties.meaning: Tesha, cho‘tdek mustahkam bola yoki kindigi cho‘t (tesha) bilan kesilgan bola

properties.name: Cho‘tir
properties.meaning: Cho‘tir, ya’ni xunuk bola. Bolani yomon ko‘zlardan asrash uchun qo‘yiladigan ism

properties.name: Cho‘tmamat
properties.meaning: Qar. Cho‘tmuhammad

properties.name: Cho‘tmat
properties.meaning: Qar. Cho‘tmuhammad

properties.name: Cho‘tmuhammad
properties.meaning: Cho‘t (tesha) dek mustahkam o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

properties.name: Cho‘tpo‘lat
properties.meaning: Cho‘t (tesha) va po‘latdek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Cho‘yan, Cho‘yanboy
properties.meaning: Cho‘yandek mustahkam bo‘lsin

properties.name: Cho‘yanbek
properties.meaning: Beklar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan cho‘yandek mustahkam bola

properties.name: Cho‘yanturdi
properties.meaning: Cho‘yandek mustahkam bo‘lib turadigan, ya’ni yashab ketadigan bola

properties.name: Cho‘yanqul
properties.meaning: Allohnig cho‘yandek mustahkam bandasi, quli

properties.name: Cho‘qmor
properties.meaning: To‘qmoq (cho‘qmor) deb mustahkam va zabardast bo‘lsin

properties.name: Cho‘qqi
properties.meaning: Hayoti qoya (cho‘qqi)dek yuksak bo‘lsin

properties.name: Cho‘g‘olboy
properties.meaning: Baquvvat, kuchli, mahkam, mustahkam bola

properties.name: Chaman
properties.meaning: Hayoti, gulzor, o‘tloqdek yashnoq bo‘lsin yoki ko‘rkam, zebo qiz yohud chamand - o‘jar, qaysar bola. Shakllari: Chamanbibi, Chamangul, Chamanoy, Chamanxon

properties.name: Chamanbibi
properties.meaning: Hayoti chamandek yashnagan, baxtiyor bola

properties.name: Chamanbuvi
properties.meaning: Go‘zal, sohibjamol qiz

properties.name: Chamanqul
properties.meaning: Gullar chamanidek zebo qiz, chamanzordek yashnoq, go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Charos
properties.meaning: Katta qora ko‘zli qiz, ko‘zlari charosdek chiroyli qiz

properties.name: Charosxon
properties.meaning: Katta qora ko‘zli qiz, ko‘zlari charosdek chiroyli qiz

properties.name: Chashma
properties.meaning: Hayoti buloq suvidek mustafo hamda davomli bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Chashmagul, Chashmaxon

properties.name: Chag‘ona
properties.meaning: Xushovoz, shirinyil, xushkalom; yoqimtoy dilkash qiz

properties.name: Chevar, Chevarxon
properties.meaning: Mohir to‘quvchi yoki to‘quvchi; qo‘li gul qiz

properties.name: Chervon, Chervonoy
properties.meaning: Qimmatli, aziz, topilmas, noyob

properties.name: Chechak
properties.meaning: Gul, maysa; go‘zal, zebo, sohibjamol. Shakllari: Chechakgul, Chechakoy

properties.name: Chechakoy
properties.meaning: Guldek zebo va oydek suluv qiz

properties.name: Chehra
properties.meaning: Yuz, jamol, ko‘rk; asli: Gulchehra (qar.)

properties.name: Chehragul
properties.meaning: Gulyuzli; chiroyli, go‘zla qiz

properties.name: Chehrashod
properties.meaning: Yuzlari kulib turgan qiz; shodon, baxtiyor

properties.name: Chilla
properties.meaning: Chilla payti (40 kunlik issiq yoki sovuq) da tug‘ilgan bola yoki chilla - kamon ipidek mahkam, mustahkam bola. Shakllari: Chillaxon

properties.name: Chimbuvi
properties.meaning: Chim (ajriqzor) dek mahkam; to‘silgan, himoyaga olingan qiz

properties.name: Chimil, Chimilxon
properties.meaning: Eht.: Chimil  -  chimir - pishiq, puxta; bosiq, vazmin

properties.name: Chimmatoy
properties.meaning: Berkilgan, yashirilgan, himoyalangan, daxlsiz qiz

properties.name: Chindaxol
properties.meaning: Bog‘langan, turmaklangan, mahkamlangan va xoldor qiz

properties.name: Chindi
properties.meaning: Jingalak, turmaklangan sochli qiz

properties.name: Chinjamol
properties.meaning: Chiroyli, sohibjamol qiz

properties.name: Chinnibahor
properties.meaning: Qar. Chinni va Bahor

properties.name: Chinniposhsha
properties.meaning: Chinniguldek zebo va baland martabali qiz

properties.name: Chinnixol
properties.meaning: Quloqlari kichkina bo‘lib yoki jingalak sochli bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Chinora
properties.meaning: Chinordek umri uzoq qiz

properties.name: Chinorbibi
properties.meaning: Umri chinordek uzoq bo‘lsin

properties.name: Chinorgul
properties.meaning: Chinor kabi uzoq umrli va guldek go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Chinsuluv
properties.meaning: Jingalak sochli yoki umrini to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Chirbonu
properties.meaning: g‘olib, muzaffar, bahodir, pahlavon

properties.name: Chirvon
properties.meaning: Qar. Chirbonu

properties.name: Chirmal
properties.meaning: Oiladagilarga chirmashib, bog‘lanib qolsin, o‘lmasin. Sol: Chirmash

properties.name: Chiroy
properties.meaning: Go‘zallik, ko‘rkamlik, go‘zal chehrali, sohibjamol

properties.name: Chiroygul
properties.meaning: Go‘zal chehrali qiz, sohibkamol, gulyuzli qiz

properties.name: Chiroyxol
properties.meaning: Xol bilan tug‘ilgan go‘zalm sohibjamol qiz

properties.name: Choygul
properties.meaning: Choyning gulidek go‘zal, yoqimli qiz. Eht.: Chiroygul (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

properties.name: Chorgul
properties.meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi qiz yoki nopok, yomon qiz. Keyingi ma’no chaqaloqni yomon ko‘zdan asrash niyatini ifodalaydi

properties.name: Chorshanbu, Chorshanbuvi
properties.meaning: Chorshanba kuni tug‘ilgan bola

properties.name: Chuchukgul
properties.meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy va guldek go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Chuchukoy
properties.meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy va oydek suluv qiz

properties.name: Chuchukxon
properties.meaning: Qar. Chuchuk (Chuchuk+xon)

properties.name: Cho‘lbibi
properties.meaning: Dashtda (cho‘lda) tug‘ilgan baland martabali qiz yoki mushtoq bo‘lib yurib erishilgan qiz

properties.name: Cho‘lponbu
properties.meaning: Iqboli baland yoki tong yulduzi Cho‘lpondek nurli, go‘zal qiz

properties.name: Cho‘lponoy
properties.meaning: Tong yulduzi Cho‘lpon va oydek go‘zal qiz yoki oydek suluv, iqboli baland qiz

properties.name: Cho‘lponxon
properties.meaning: Cho‘lpon yulduzidek go‘zal va baland martabali, e’zozli qiz

properties.name: Cho‘ri
properties.meaning: Qul, xizmatkori qiz

properties.name: Cho‘ribibi
properties.meaning: Qar. Cho‘ri (Cho‘ri+bibi)
